      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫55 / GID</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X47333AeG_-DKzNNgBTQeQYF3JAXhdHw1pK3WxrdYB3uA70GYhkPFOj6s4QFzaOFc5-PO2KNFWPHoqPEkWTaz-4IX1vXy7KQMTSef-bXwMTmeKbrvOm5gqS1bWAYDO3SkERLstdAWiVafTrMii3IUgNADvT6yZ2czsoquYSpAfI1gE3uQMpft2lHQgGoJw9g4uo-rE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lambeth, Streatham Hill SW16<br><br>55 now also known as GID (Getting It Done) are a small street gang based on the Mountearl Gardens, Sackville and Leigham Court estates in Streatham, within the SW16 postcode. 55 are allied with 674, 55, 417, ABM, BG, Harlem, KuKu, Mitcham and Gipsy Hill. They come into conflicts with 150, 410, 031, 17, 37, SIRU, Uptop, Claptown and Roadside.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Trapmash / S5 / Bugzface / S Money]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2701-122</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
