      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>LxDrive</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Wandsworth, Roehampton SW15<br><br>LxDrive are a small street gang who are based the Lennox estate in Roehampton, within the SW15 postcode. They are allied with 213/Sutton.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Dbandsz]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-817717-2701-77</styleUrl>
