      <Placemark>
        <name>Pollards Hill</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Merton, Pollards Hill CR4<br><br>The Pollards Hill gang are based around South Lodge Avenue on the Pollards Hill estate, within the CR4 postcode. The area is closely affiliated with nearby Mitcham,  and from the mid to late 2000s 'Pollards Mandem' (PMD) were under the influence of the 'Terrorzone' (TZ) gang from Mitcham. They were known as 'Money Never sleeps' (MNS) during much of the 2010s, but since the late 2010s they have been known simply as Pollards Hill, and they are loosely allied with 417, 674, 55/GID, LTH and ABM.  They beef with CR7, SIRU, 37, 17, Claptown, Fudgetown and former allies Mitcham.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Trigz / D Speng / Marga S]]></description>
