      <Placemark>
        <name>🟣Silwood / SyriaS</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4RiFktymwlPn7U4M7B8cOvrKXN8sTUD-n2eGa-GgS1ci819GFG_EEjotr8bqgPO0cjuJBucyJNuvrtfNx3s7IdlUrwIBVn7DVvuKwblGXY75A-egrzm02P8JLWuC8AaKUdXmO83j5WcK3pzV6-bLAuUeflZyZ3C4ZrqYkXjL7iB0VAAwJ-uxYrkBjjePWXusUa9fQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Boroughs of Southwark and Lewisham, Rotherithe SE16<br><br>Silwood Nation are a small street gang who are based on the Silwood estate in South Bermondsey, straddling both the borders of Lewisham and Southwark. Historically the Silwood estate has been referred to as "Burn Block". The younger generation are known as 'SyriaS'. They are allied with Monson and Lovelinch. They beef with Ghetto, BSide, Block 6, PR15 and JRoad.<br><br>Associated Rappers} AMiz / T1 / Trigga T / RS / YA]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-9C27B0-2701-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4RiFktymwlPn7U4M7B8cOvrKXN8sTUD-n2eGa-GgS1ci819GFG_EEjotr8bqgPO0cjuJBucyJNuvrtfNx3s7IdlUrwIBVn7DVvuKwblGXY75A-egrzm02P8JLWuC8AaKUdXmO83j5WcK3pzV6-bLAuUeflZyZ3C4ZrqYkXjL7iB0VAAwJ-uxYrkBjjePWXusUa9fQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
