      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Block 6

https://web.archive.org/web/20111011120534/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/catford-wildcats</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7rAIKHTgw7X0rXOZtriWhVCQ3QVjCQeiJrEftCuvYjedH3XbJbVC71s-gScUBrqznBf01O9hJNS2NycDIFo3FSM0Imwy_cgUetM8MgJZzKHz_hSReVPw0xbwY6SfOWnAkKplxhtC9o1J-63748FyiM7fIkQrPcXSPsse71FBZUW90br_qvV8IQVmNCfH3D83jWZXI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lewisham, Catford SE6<br><br>Block 6 are a large street gang based on the Milford Towers estate in Catford, within the SE6 postcode. Second and third generations of 'Ghetto Boys' from Catford became their own independent gang in the 1990s, known as 'Catford Wildcats' (CWC), or sometimes 'Wildkatz'.  Following a split within the 'Ghetto Boys' in the mid 2000s,  Catford became engaged in the bitter rivalry with the New Cross 'Ghetto Boys', known as the 'Shower' gang. Wildcats then became known as the 'Anti Shower' gang, or simply 'Anti' as their antagonistic response to the 'Shower' gang. They would beef with Ghetto, Turnham and Penge, as well as the Ferrier Boys. By 2010 the younger generation of 'Anti Shower' were known as 'Black Hand' and were closely affiliated with 'Black Mafia'. Both identified with the colour black. By early 2010s the gang had became more commonly known as 'Block 6' and had deaded the beef with Ghetto and Turnham with their main conflict now being with M20 and SG. For most of the 2010s Block 6 were allied with BSide, Block 12 and Ghetto. By the late 2010s some Block 6 members began to have issues with allies BSide, which had caused issues within the gang.  This would result in Block 6 members who had issues with BSide leaving the gangs and setting up new sets. They beef with SG, M20, Monson, 4Anti BlueHills, WildBatch and North Heath.<br><br>The newer younger generations are allied with CR0 and the Splashset from Croydon. They beef with the LDG/BlueHillz, Monson, Linch, 4Anti, 6thStreet, Ghetto, Turnham, M20, SG, BSide, Block12, AMO and Silwood gangs.<br><br>Associated Rappers} A6 / Ghostface / YA / Lucii / Tzgwala / Jooka]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2501-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
