      <Placemark>
        <name>Block12 / 124 / AWC / HTN</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Downham SE6<br><br>Block12, also known as 124, are a small street gang from the Downham area, within the SE6 postcode. Their original name of 124 is taken from the number 124 London bus route which runs through their gangs territory. They are allied with Block 6, Ghetto and Turnham. They were also closely allied with BSide but the two are now in conflict. They beef SG, M20 and former allies BSide.<br><br>AWC/HTN are two new small sets who are based around the Downham area of Lewisham, within the SE6 postcode. They are allied with 6thStreet. They beef with LDG/BlueHillz, Block 6, M20 and Turnham.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Pistol (Block 12) / Skyz (Block 12) / Lz (Block 12) / Skizzy / KayGrab / MSlapit / D1 / Gwopz]]></description>
