      <Placemark>
        <name>BSide / 785</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Bellingham SE6<br><br>BSide are a street gang from the Bellingham area, within the SE6 postcode. They are also known as "785". They are allied with Ghetto, Block 6, BlueHillz, Turnham and 26.  BSide were once also allied with Block 12 but the two are now in conflict. They beef with M20, SG, Monson, Silwood, O'Lanna, Block 12 and Zone 2.<br><br>The younger generation are allied with nearby LDG/BlueHillz, Turnham and 4Anti. They beef Block 6, AMO, 6thStreet, Block 12, O'Lanna, Silwood, Monson, M20, SG and Ghetto.<br><br>Associated Rappers} 30 / KK / Django / Dizz / Bgod / Lil D / Msavv / Rex / Splitsplash / Munch / Rsz]]></description>
