      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵STK / STown / LPW</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6cmjaZXwOHfnXk_AV2qhMXBCWnnYeh-Y7GxJ0ux5ZANqa1ytQ-BXP4CDMlLtYuP6oKfAITOYYMFzqkoDJdaCBHJlPrO7IUj0Gs16_4M75aYjI84zEzenbqOgDTACR2D1hXVxvsjJD2V6FdMS0Ejv0M38M49lytI7Q3CQ3k6q0qWaJl4mRYredLxieN4YnYKl4STaq-25eWBzR3VwlS-QqYoeZHTDGp_FVsybdW3gH-g_r-?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Shirley CR0<br><br>STK/STown are a street gang based on the Shrublands estate in the Shirley area of Croydon, within the CR0 postcode. They are part of the LPW (Little Patch World) alliance who identify with the colour blue. They are allied with 5th, VP SBV and CR7. They beef with CR0, Fieldway and MH.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Lil Prezi / Yucky / TapeDat / Msav / Splash / KP]]></description>
