      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵SG</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6pXimeXZ8RSwdW3b5nrW279iGeaGroxrUaHnmQY7ybwe1AQXCxHcqGbXh_d5BotZdlDykh8lw_rmArRMt3UZS4B8QMZrCFK_oF4blgTrlkLFUPaWmFchW_PzO-rohXJ4oQWDevBkVojGtJu9dzmCQdBvkRShqtcni0FZSst0WEFU5UXQaQ67HbIZtfs9l07OAUGD8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lewisham, Grove Park SE9/SE12<br><br>SG are a street gang who are based in the Grove Park area of Lewisham, straddling the border of both Lewisham and Greenwich boroughs within both SE9 and SE12 postcodes. The gangs main base is the Chinbrook estate, but they are also active around the Marbrook Close, Henry Cooper Way, Sandstone Road and Wydeville Manor Road estates. Their SG name can be translated as ‘Splash Gang’, ‘Strally Gang’ or ‘Shankers & Gunners’.  SG formed during the mid 2000s and identify with dark blue colours. In their early years they were allied with their now rivals Turnham. They beef BSide, Ghetto, Block 6, BlueHills, Turnham, Block 12, O'Lanna, and 26.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Reeko Squeeze / Teddy / S2H / Slaughter / Blocks]]></description>
