        <name>⚫PR15 / NBR</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4lmbNvfRoq2hLYcAkPeYj5DazACYl4ejD1KyN7uOYXYu4-ezTZUM5zjEtJ3Nzh4_3NVoMUs4xU0i7kBScgL38Px7cSAHTk8kDqdg8fTt1ArR3V-6M0QlW6oXmDIMqd_CLixLkfFjsdGD4XBeQtEtX2Jgsxm-w9axHCAVD3ogQ-dfgPukKCMNmDEMTgswfzN4fsU2Q?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Southwark, Peckham SE15<br><br>PR15/NBR are a small street gang who are based in the Peckham Rye area.]]></description>
