      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Roadside / Block 5 / 198

https://web.archive.org/web/20120103014818/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/roadside-gs</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4i-m47L4-pvfkjmxnZAl8yIBSH0bUdOI9Na9rHQVVQWoD8UjtHv0ptpM4Al109PpLb8jI7FMKK7bb1csnOuAboRLZRSZZtdxvMuDuaKV1K-aB9zb4nXarRUQy-AUNsecRLNfPb_UvYY9l7NlGKkM-CcpmsA89yt3JsNqxJRpb_-ct8q8gh93-GfBxmGdYRhisjTt8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Boroughs of Lambeth and Southwark, Brixton and Camberwell SW9/SE5<br><br>Roadside (RSG) are a street gang who are based around the Brixton and Camberwell area, on estates along Coldharbour Lane on border of Lambeth and Southwark boroughs, within both SW9 and SE5 postcodes. The gang are situated on the Thorlands, Crawford and Lilford estates. They are known by the acronyms RSG (Roadside Gs), or YRS (Young Roadside) and TRS (Tiny Roadside) although also known as Block 5 or C-Block (Crawford estate). Roadside have had a long rivalry with the 'Peckham Boys'.  This is despite the fact that some of the gangs elder members have relatives in the  'Peckham Boys'. They were affiliated with fellow Brixton gang PDC and were part of the "031 Bloods" alliance in Lambeth with allies 031 and CFR. The younger generations (YRS and TRS) were affiliated with their fellow Brixton based gangs GAS, OC and SIRU.  Over the years the main rivals of Roadside have been Peckham, Tulse Hill (TN1), and Stockwell (ABM). During the early 2010s the 'Block 5' name has become more prominent and is the name most commonly used by the gangs current generation. They are loosely affiliated with 150, 410, 031, 17, 37, Uptop and Claptown.<br><br>Associated Rappers} RA / Levelz / MVM / Riotz / Kenzay / Kash Malone]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2801-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4i-m47L4-pvfkjmxnZAl8yIBSH0bUdOI9Na9rHQVVQWoD8UjtHv0ptpM4Al109PpLb8jI7FMKK7bb1csnOuAboRLZRSZZtdxvMuDuaKV1K-aB9zb4nXarRUQy-AUNsecRLNfPb_UvYY9l7NlGKkM-CcpmsA89yt3JsNqxJRpb_-ct8q8gh93-GfBxmGdYRhisjTt8?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
