      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢M20 / KTA</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4hghvd-xP_hzdhTTN9kjt4BKPi93zeOb7-LuvS2tsB_3Q5VYwydwfxVnEw2N-rk9TS70gPKWJoj8f7XvpdI7l3KFKrqU8_3caibw6mDwA6dmgG6Z1KKi4boVzHaQO9AYtm5QD7VjKHR2Y_ZSXqfzRj0xIewnl2YsBFhVed2ICQedrhv1XXLzdDaH9AjXcJQKdrHHM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Bromley, Penge SE20<br><br>M20 are a large street gang based in Penge, within the SE20 postcode. M20 were formed following a merger of two local groups from Penge known as Murder Squad (MS) and Block 20 (B20). These affiliated Penge sets made up the youngest generations who followed on from older Penge sets such as "Squeeze Section" and "P-Block" who had been active during the 2000s and early 2010s. Penge gangs are allied with CR0 and at one time were also linked up with SG/SMG sets. M20 are known for rivalry with most gangs in Lewisham, notably with Ghetto, Turnham, BSide, Block 6, LDG/BlueHills, 26, 5th, Block 12, O'Lanna and NoMannerz.<br><br>Associated Rappers} CH/C2 / Bugzy / ST / YS]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-7CB342-2801-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4hghvd-xP_hzdhTTN9kjt4BKPi93zeOb7-LuvS2tsB_3Q5VYwydwfxVnEw2N-rk9TS70gPKWJoj8f7XvpdI7l3KFKrqU8_3caibw6mDwA6dmgG6Z1KKi4boVzHaQO9AYtm5QD7VjKHR2Y_ZSXqfzRj0xIewnl2YsBFhVed2ICQedrhv1XXLzdDaH9AjXcJQKdrHHM?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
