      <Placemark>
        <name>🔘Brooklyn / OBY / BFR / OKR / NOB

https://web.archive.org/web/20110602134407/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/brooklyn</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5FGL0C-lb_BVBWF-TyQ0RMnQ_ATa4MVdGZjDYyQxFMzIxcjQUV1MTnUOkcV_yLPJW75vMu_smt-kKgb6GWA7kImWx4sFe3_0YXtonY5ZKLjQSEtqYfszWCt50VKrdvx3IC5ItcEXRZLBOXYiz_xT2mjsJ08ckzkf1DB8lJrfey_hBsg4ya1j1qNY63QjD1RlJOGS8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Southwark, Old Kent Road SE1<br><br>Brooklyn are a street gang based around the Old Kent Road on the Mawbey and Avondale Square estates and also new build estates around Abercorn Way, situated within the SE1 postcode. Brooklyn is a name given to the estates situated to the north of Old Kent Road. The Brooklyn gang formed in the mid 2000s and identify with dark grey colours. Brooklyn have also been known by names, such as 'Original Brooklyn Youths' (OBY) and 'Brooklyn Family Riders' (BFR). The gang had in their early years also been referred to as GME which primarily stood for 'Get Money Early' or 'Give Me Everything'. Brooklyn were at one time affiliated with the 'Peckham Boys' although by 2008 the two areas had fallen into conflict, with 'Peckham Boys' insultingly describing Brooklyn as Peckham rejects.  Through their rivalry with Peckham, Brooklyn would become closely allied with the Brixton gangs especially GAS and OC, who were also heavily beefing with Peckham during the late 2000s. Their alliances with Brixton had also brought an affiliation with the Brixton allies, 031 from Stockwell. The beef between Brooklyn/Brixton against 'Peckham Boys' has since died down. The gang now go by OKR which stands for Old Kent Road or as NOB which stands for North of Burgess<br><br>Associated Rappers} Johnny Gunz/John Wayne / Timbo / Cass / Mitch]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-424242-2401-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
