      <Placemark>
        <name>MH</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Croydon, Monks Hill CR2<br><br>MH (Money Habits) are a small street gang who are based on the Monks Hill estate in the Selsdon area located in the south of Croydon, within the CR2 postcode. They are allied with Fieldway. They beef STK.<br><br>Associated Rappers} JMulla / Rowdy / MH Baby]]></description>
