        <name>⚫ROC / Rockingham / 063</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Southwark, Elephant & Castle SE1<br><br>ROC are a street gang based on the Rockingham estate in Elephant & Castle, within the SE1 postcode. They tend to be allied with Harlem, KuKu and Moscow17.]]></description>
