      <Placemark>
        <name>YTB / 061</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Southwark, Southwark SE1<br><br>061 are a small street gang who are based on the Tabard Gardens estate in Bermondsey,  within the SE1 postcode. They come into conflicts with Harlem, KuKu, Moscow 17, Browning17 and AY17.]]></description>
