      <Placemark>
        <name>🔘Aylesbury17 (AY17)

https://web.archive.org/web/20110602072158/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/wooly-hood</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4UFzP3jvvDZZYeoY2yauKqMmYBVeYocJWGXTDMKzyyMGE66IzaGGZzwRZQnvMOxH56ItnDeRk5DpAHTUrOwIDEKACDOTQVjjs3QVOY3Z92tiRcSjdgk5r6K8Ldnn2InDw5YNJ5Krq2Dj83eAm1iFEMmW7gYmQq3qX7OutkLJ7gqQ0FSvjQ38hdoFuB9qu7NkytOEY?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Southwark, Walworth SE17<br><br>AY17 are a small street gang based on the Aylesbury estate in Walworth, within the SE17 postcode. They are also known as 'Suicide Squad'. The area is currently undergoing a major regeneration programme with much of the Aylesbury estate largest blocks due to be demolished. Previous gangs of the Walworth area were known under different names including 'Ratchets' and from 2004/05 the OTB acronym which can be interpreted as 'Out To Ball' or 'Out To Bade' has been around, although is now more related to the music side of things, as they are now an older generation. In the 2000s other cliques included 'Mandem on Brandon' (MOB) and 'Criminally Gifted' (CG), whilst more generic names have included Wooly Road Mandem and Wooly Hood. The Wooly Hood sets have been closely allied with the nearby Peckham Boys for many years and have shared many of the same rivals and allies as them although the relationships between Walworth and Peckham have became more contentious after the new and youngest generations from both areas fell into serious conflict during 2015/16 although the older generations remain close allies. The 'Shoot Instant' (SI) set of the Peckham Boys were active on the Aylesbury estate during the 2000 and the early 2010s when the Peckham Boys controlled the area. AY17 are allied with nearby Browning17, Moscow17, Harlem and KuKu. The gang beef Zone 2, YPB, CMB, 410, 150, 17, Uptop, Claptown and China Walk.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-757575-2801-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4UFzP3jvvDZZYeoY2yauKqMmYBVeYocJWGXTDMKzyyMGE66IzaGGZzwRZQnvMOxH56ItnDeRk5DpAHTUrOwIDEKACDOTQVjjs3QVOY3Z92tiRcSjdgk5r6K8Ldnn2InDw5YNJ5Krq2Dj83eAm1iFEMmW7gYmQq3qX7OutkLJ7gqQ0FSvjQ38hdoFuB9qu7NkytOEY?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
