      <Placemark>
        <name>SRoad</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Greenwich, Shooters Hill SE18<br><br>SRoad are a small street gang who are based around the Shooters Hill Road in the Shooters Hill area of Greenwich, within the SE18 postcode. They are allied with Cherry. The gang beef WildBatch, Ferrier, WoolyO and GS28.<br><br>Associated Rappers} C Rose / D Duppy / L'Smoko / Dc]]></description>
