      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵VP / 430 / LPW</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7Wb7fiRTb0RcUWXuop9OdisX2c7KERc-ZtG0EcqfUkJ0yvFAufH9RI720xrlaqAzQlSN_ovhrjXvTI4L7gxNFPUoFNh20w4gQDh75WQnPQ2o_ayxkdK1oz4lYrbJHm7Wp9z5iLtncDljrLb0US-Dhf0O6SMF7QqIujDrfr-MtxFRBs9A1rkKiaOsSpCi_Y6uqBwDQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Croydon CR0<br><br>VP (Valley Park), also known as '430' and sometimes the 'Parkers', are a street gang based on the Franklin Way estate in the Valley Park area of Croydon, within the CR0 postcode. They are part of the LPW (Little Patch World) alliance who identify with the colour blue. They are allied with 5th, SBV, STK and CR7. They beef with CR0 and Fieldway.<br><br>Associated Rappers} SL / B1 / YingYang / YuckyTugg / Droptop]]></description>
