      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫🔴CR0 / DSN / 00

https://web.archive.org/web/20120423130632/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/don-t-say-nothin-dsn</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7maFNP2SzlkiEDHpteuij1AT9EciQoWts6-3Ggvb2tXdH0kEegXBTF-wnY_I8gg5BlaJtII2ZWA6P_O4rU8uc-TWjdWsFHRNafQqNiwH5jYhTrmsaT0TfwXnljGAIzQQ8T7-rzUQO6VyaKEOCv2_pGuuX8-_NX4aTgetp62SNmqA_om-bUoFNhMRnrhkhnaxccTbU?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Croydon CR0<br><br>CR0, formerly known as DSN (Don’t Say Nothin), are a street gang from Croydon, around the town centre, including North End and Waddon, within the CR0 postcode. The gang began around 2004/2005 and grew in response to attacks on local Croydon youths by members of the 'Gipset' and Dogs To Kill (D2K) gangs from the nearby Gipsy Hill and Thornton Heath areas. In 2006 DSN had became closely associated with the Byrdgang clique composed of gang members who had links between Brixton and Croydon,  and by 2009/10 the DSN and Byrdgang sets were one and the same. The original younger generation of DSN were known as D2M (Down 2 Murder), or Y.DSN. The rapid growth of DSN soon led to the fierce rivalry with Shine My Nine (SMN) from the Thornton Heath area as well as 'Gipset' from the Gipsy Hill area. DSN gang recruited predominantly from the estates surrounding Croydon centre and also North End, Broad Green and Waddon, including the local estates around Handcroft Road, Parsons Mead, Ruskin Road and Whitehorse Road. By 2006 DSN declared Croydon town centre as their turf and the High Streets and shopping centre would become the scene of frequent violent clashes,  involving their rivals from 'Shine My Nine', 'Gipset' and 'Block Cartel'. DSN were originally allied with 'Squeeze Section' and 'GMG' from both Croydon and Penge and 'Anti/Shower' from Catford. They also had ties with 031 from Stockwell, notably the 'Killa Gangsta Bloods' (KGB), from South Lambeth. Their current generations are allied with Fieldway, M20 and Block 6. Their main rivals are CR7, VP, 5th, STK and SBV.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Floss / Tuggzy / MTrap / JoJo Hundred / Baby'0 / Wholagun / Bully]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2901-117</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7maFNP2SzlkiEDHpteuij1AT9EciQoWts6-3Ggvb2tXdH0kEegXBTF-wnY_I8gg5BlaJtII2ZWA6P_O4rU8uc-TWjdWsFHRNafQqNiwH5jYhTrmsaT0TfwXnljGAIzQQ8T7-rzUQO6VyaKEOCv2_pGuuX8-_NX4aTgetp62SNmqA_om-bUoFNhMRnrhkhnaxccTbU?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
