      <Placemark>
        <name>🟣WildBatch</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4v8wdOXWnOFafmV9RgGF3OckgsiHqx62RRtFq4exPz-2let82KopG2cU4MMqT5RBWYQyLtZL3z90vbZKJt68P37PUEcStq4_LrJu3tCdUeldgEMkh8AkU45UK-7qDjCfJeKdyJMnxC4oPo6k6hqHyxCPJ222Zgt9p4S9vn4Uk9o9E0YuAohyk-vzflW9NdG2l28VM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Greenwich, Woolwich SE18<br><br>WildBatch are a street gang based around Woolwich, within the SE18 postcode. They are mostly active on the Barnfield, Woolwich Common and Nightingale estates. They have the subset called '18Hunna' based on the Barnfield estate. They beef nearby WoolyO, Cherry, SRoad, GS28, Parkside, Block 6, 9Side, FYG and North Heath.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Zico / Lil D££ King / Shawaa / 18 Sav / Denzo / 3Dee / LZino]]></description>
