      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵5th / LPW</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4lyj_geAgeAMzNsFkVFQsGUr838MzzOQopCLlteCMKQbVBCPI9ETSMZnALp36tr5W0BSWT5POrTIauyBonME_zostcbKH34U29FFu-1ss8Pxo4wcBYOuhfH_I0mBUP8J9dOez4Qdv8v4bNH16-yX3ae9xSyqnzOvu3F6iQwz_IsxWVQbN1CS7F_GWov0OHRexDWQm5TMTp1sknAqbuUiHNHsgX59HQuBQM8M-0bvZD1e7N?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, South Norwood SE25<br><br>5th are a street gang based around the South Norwood area, within the SE25 postcode. They are part of LPW (Little Patch World) alliance who identify with the colour of blue. They are allied with VP, SBV, STK and CR7. They beef with nearby CR0, Fieldway and M20.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Teeway / 5ive]]></description>
