      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Lovelinch</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, New Cross SE15<br><br>Lovelinch are a small street gang based on the Lovelinch estate located between the area of New Cross and South Bermondsey, within the SE15 postcode. They beef Ghetto, whilst they are allied with Monson and Silwood.]]></description>
