      <Placemark>
        <name>26 / Upper Sydenham</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Sydenham SE26<br><br>26 consists of small sets based around Sydenham, within the SE26 postcode. Sydenham is split between upper Sydenham and lower Sydenham.  They are loosely allied with BSide and LDG/BlueHillz. They beef with M20 and SG.]]></description>
