      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢9Side</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6df98GWC5ZjcJ5EiR_RSTv1rVaDJ-sjf3BpFf_DYUlujStAwOg6y-ODHppO6KwSMAqs-hDs4ZoPTcKKVv690HVr4pek3cj6JCZfR0vx7dcJZxiGiRvBbp9bnx2HhzOFYSaJDJsia5csRKTOgm_MJA317_B1XY6Kr6mZeJDO1VZUEu7SCttpkhdmWKmvRtqOav3kBQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Greenwich, Eltham SE9<br><br>9Side are a small street gang who are active on Middle Park avenue estates in Eltham, within the SE9 postcode. They are descended from the 'Ferrier Boys' following the relocation of Ferrier gang members into the area during the demolition of the Ferrier estate between 2009-2012. '9Side' are allied with WoolyO and M9. They beef with Ferrier and WildBatch.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Swarmz]]></description>
