      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫🟢Parkside</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Bexley, Belvedere DA17<br><br>Parkside are a small street gang based around the Belvedere and Erith area of Bexley Borough, especially the blocks in and around the Upper Abbey Road and Picardy Street areas. They are allied with GS28 and FYG. They beef with AWB, West Street, WoolyO and Wildbatch.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Kage / NoToss / Tragic / Spooks]]></description>
