      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵⚫SProf / SP / S16</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Bexley, Welling DA16<br><br>SProf are a street gang based on the John Newton estate in Welling, within the DA16 postcode. They have taken over from a somewhat now extinct gang knows as GH00, pronounced GHunna. GH00 have been taken over by 'SProf', also known as 'SP' (Strictly Profit). They are identidy with blue and black colours and are allied with WC/1800. They beef WildBatch while GH00 had beef with North Heath.<br><br>Associated Rappers} TSav (SProf) / 2Fourz (SProf) / Bandit (SProf) / KM (SProf) / JTapz (SProf) / KD (SProf) / KM (SProf) Cheeko Lion (GH00) / CsOrCrase (GH00)]]></description>
