      <Placemark>
        <name>4Anti</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Brockley SE4<br><br>4Anti are a street gang based on several small estates in the Brockley area known as 'Brocktown' within the SE4 postcode area. They are allied with Turnham and BSide. They beef with AWC, LDG, 6thStreet, Block 6, Ghetto, T1D, PR15, M20, SG, LoveLinch, Monson, DQN and JRoad.<br><br>Associated Rappers} G2 / Greeko / Chingface / JB]]></description>
