      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵LDG / BlueHillz / 2300</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5DxVfmIFWMzYDZEggBrugttDA-eGVe0FscSQ6DgF-Dx8C7VFSGLiufaAGdL8yVAOeYU4_BG-SlX7BEkppDB8SLcCrYyboALMLMJeOcO8lSWSVmVfSO80smWTveBI6yb1pWcUpBnkC1F-PN7hMemClrXMCcCV9RgeqswGtmly0dsRpMTmgDNpoXzk9hEmWzbj8wUiI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lewisham, Forest Hill SE23<br><br>LDG/BlueHillz/2300 are sets based on several small estates in the Forest Hill area, within the SE23 postcode. 'LDG/2300' originally formed as a younger generation of 'BlueHillz'. They are allied with BSide and 26. They beef Block 6, M20 and SG.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Ksav / Stacka / Switch / Pokez / Lil Aone / HR / JLoose / SLoose / Hazard / YPizzac / Tizz]]></description>
