        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lambeth, Vauxhall SW8<br><br>VCity are a small street gang based on the Ashmole estate in the Vauxhall area within the SW8 postcode. VCity are new set allied with nearby Harlem, KuKu, Moscow17, Browning17 and AY17. Nearby Harlem and KuKu members are known to often chill on this block.]]></description>
