        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4oprEuEdCrIiPiLbGsFgfDctwdJI5BUEk_AQ_x4P1pnNWfVjn9dV6XQdMvwIyOdXlHLE6Qt7kKRqnJkVEC_T1Q86dIqUxCzrZLNr3uAqd4MBwi8UQU00fZI2X6BW8CLhK5cvYjT593nMJ1iQRQ2x0ndO0qZK1yj8VrkwXga7sPzRtKNmPqX0VHRWx8GiHmCv-Pymq1?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Thornton Heath CR0/CR7<br><br>SplashSet are a small street gang based around Bensham Lane in the Thornton Heath area of Croydon straddling the CR0 and CR7 postcodes. They are allied with nearby GLane and Block 6. They beef with STK, SBV, 5th, VP, Waddon, M20, KWO and 25.<br><br>Associated Rappers} RumDat / Jloose]]></description>
