        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5s1R18LngOi6PsoVFb9Qpcl-al4khW9VPapb3A-P-QPR5Oc5LzvLOwOUCtjNslD1TQeCpCY4oQcH1itGeQGkFCTISb3x0trowssTVbhlnAN5DrBjVCHagIVHnxa36X_vhDe8MJeRb1mZaoLotfK1UDH2Of3wBYRbL0JxagJ7kmohBIVWMIm9EPmizqzAUMdPRgBpzn?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lambeth, Brixton Hill SW2<br><br>MFL (Mafia Lane) are a set based on the St Matthews estate in the Brixton Hill area, within the SW2 postcode. They are cliqued up with nearby YND. They also have loose ties with 674, RP, 55, ABM, 417, BG, Harlem, KuKu, Mitcham and Gipsy Hill. They have beef with 150, 410, Uptop, Claptown, CMB, 17 and 37.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Notorious S / MrW1ck]]></description>
