      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Cherry / OCB / YCB / 04TM / Redside</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X41P8RXuGgtQr5eWxK6MyiAO_kk8bKp0POcFj2Mh6z8zWf_A26oSRWPK0ljUmUj36VzJFAHKUCGKpobyeayyCk8mvXgE_K-EUWD5swUYGSb_OOpYVtSafBVOHLSM_Sn-Jx9YXcZVlJ1vp2miRZ-lbeQ1MnmpeZ58E3eWsNeetbOky94YBMvDI1pzUHQ_crZTvDLwIU6?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Greenwich, Charlton SE7<br><br>The Cherry Boys are a street gang based on Cherry Orchard and Springfield Grove estates in Charlton, located within the SE7 postcode area. They identify as Bloods, and refer to the area of Charlton as "Redtown".  Sub-divisions have included both 'Original Cherry Boys' (OCB), and 'Cherry Young Bloods' (CYB).  They beef Ferrier, GS28, CGM and WoolyO. They had also in their early years came into conflict with Ghetto.<br><br>The newest generation have started going by 04TM or Redside. They have inherited the beef from older generations. They are allied with Monson, Silwood, SRoad, H-Block and ARB. They beef CGM, WildBatch, WoolyO, AWB, GS28 and YCB.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Lucky Lavish / Kronez / 2fourz / AK / Movi / Stainer / Creepz / Killa Shak]]></description>
