      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴AWB</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Boroughs of Greenwich and Bexley, Abbey Wood SE2<br><br>AWB (Abbey Wood Boys) are a small street gang who are based on the Woolwich and Erith estate and the Thistlebrook traveller site in the Abbey Wood area, within the SE2 postcode. They beef GS28, FYG, Parkside, Cherry and North Heath.]]></description>
