      <Placemark>
        <name>Uptop / UTH</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lambeth, Upper Tulse Hill SW2<br><br>Uptop are a street gang based on the St Martins estate in the Upper Tulse Hill area, within the SW2 postcode. They are also known as UTH (Upper Tulse Hill). In the 2000s Tulse Hill were referred to as 'Tulse Hill Mandem' whilst some used the name 'T-Block'. In the 1990s and the early 2000s Tulse Hill tended to align themselves with Brixton gangs like the 28s, PDC and NS, whilst Upper Tulse Hill also had affiliations with Gipsy Hill and West Norwood. Around 2008/09 Lower Tulse Hill (TN1) would start to beef Brixton, which divided Tulse Hill with Upper Tulse Hill siding with Brixton.  They are allied with 150, 410, 031, 17, 37 and Claptown.  They beef 674, LTH, 55, 417, KuKu, Harlem, SIRU, ABM, Gipsy Hill, Moscow17, Browning17 and AY17.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Mayhem / RB / Shuuds / SmokeyJack / KillBill ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-757575-2801-77</styleUrl>
