      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫674</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5HNYH4G5ExFxIpKOIU1S6KvNfi7F7_FEJftDZk9MMq6DIDCj4IxbTFfy6_RKmonIhQt3zYu_X0w9u9jkYWjnan3GBb9AvW1V5-tG2GJFAKH5oZhQdBOsBGDCcvST3gDEsxKSTsohmwLTb7N_ujgB_H20CbknjUXhVbCDiiXiB3PsoVg16tbF5TKIYvYJOZocN8NSo?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lambeth, Brixton Hill SW2/SW4<br><br>674 (often known simply as 67) are a large street gang who are based around New Park Road on the Clapham Park and Roupell Park estates in Brixton Hill within the SW2 and SW4 postcodes.<br><br>The '674' gang name has been in use since the early 2010s. Before this Brixton Hill went by OSG (On Sight Gang) and as BHB (Brixton Hill Bloods/Brixton Hill Bullies), while the other Brixton Hill sets of late 2000s and early 2010s had included NPG (New Park Gunners), P1O (Parks 1st Originals) and the 'Marga Lane' gang. The gang name of '674' derives from the keypad on a trap phone which reflects the previous name of 'OSG' (where 6=O, 7=S and 4=G).  '674' on a keypad can also reflect 'NPG' (New Park Gunners), However they usually just shorten it to simply '67'. Along with other Brixton groups like 150 and 410 they are considered the pioneers of the UK Drill scene.<br><br><br> 674 are closely allied with nearby LTH and 55 in an alliance often referred to as the "Hillside" alliance consisting of the Brixton Hill, Tulse Hill and Streatham Hill area. The alliance sometimes includes Gipsy Hill as well. They are allied with LTH, 55, Gipsy Hill, ABM, 417, Mitcham, Harlem and KuKu. They beef 150, 410, 031, 17, 37, SIRU, Uptop, Claptown and Roadside.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Scribz/LD / Dimzy / Monkey / ASAP / Liquez / SJ / R6 / ST / Itch / Dopesmoke / Silent]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2701-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5HNYH4G5ExFxIpKOIU1S6KvNfi7F7_FEJftDZk9MMq6DIDCj4IxbTFfy6_RKmonIhQt3zYu_X0w9u9jkYWjnan3GBb9AvW1V5-tG2GJFAKH5oZhQdBOsBGDCcvST3gDEsxKSTsohmwLTb7N_ujgB_H20CbknjUXhVbCDiiXiB3PsoVg16tbF5TKIYvYJOZocN8NSo?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
