      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Monson

https://web.archive.org/web/20111011215437/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/monson-bloodset</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X69lv0sawjHMhTvcGDQQi7Fe1JXK4qE0OtO5T9-Gq3jl7EKiqNjz67_iiQ6KM47-nJsUpTbmyZZT5x6MK65NzkxxGW1jiBu6WfKq7Dzgk_o024HeB68jMrwjstNe7Ix1vq5U4VcAYhqgcWWfZXwYkWnRQeHWi712GyzDdIdlUn2Bp2w_5dlVFd9RTaoyBabemiY-WWR?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lewisham, New Cross Gate SE14<br><br>Monson are a street gang based on the Monson estate and surrounding blocks in the New Cross Gate area, around the border of the boroughs of Lewisham and Southwark, within the SE14 postcode. Monson formed around 2006/07. They identified as Bloods, and were known as 'Monson Bloodset' (MB), or 'Young Monson Bloodset' (YMB). Monsons current generation are referred to as 'MTown' or 'MT14' whilst some go by GST (Gate Side Thugs).  The gang continue to identify with the colour red, although not necessarily now as Bloods. Prior to the Monson gang forming there was criminal street collectives in the area but did not always have a gang name. New Cross Gate lies between two of the cities largest, most reputed, gang territories, with 'Peckham' to the west and the 'Ghetto Boys' to the east.  Their close proximity to Peckham may have been a reason for 'Monson' not becoming 'Ghetto Boys', because New Cross Gate was considered dangerous territory for the 'Ghetto Boys' due to their close proximity to Peckham. They are allied with Silwood, YPB, Claptown, 17 and Lovelinch. They beef nearby Ghetto, Block 6, Turnham, Brooklyn and Harlem.<br><br>Associated Rappers} DTR4P / MBG]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2501-122</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X69lv0sawjHMhTvcGDQQi7Fe1JXK4qE0OtO5T9-Gq3jl7EKiqNjz67_iiQ6KM47-nJsUpTbmyZZT5x6MK65NzkxxGW1jiBu6WfKq7Dzgk_o024HeB68jMrwjstNe7Ix1vq5U4VcAYhqgcWWfZXwYkWnRQeHWi712GyzDdIdlUn2Bp2w_5dlVFd9RTaoyBabemiY-WWR?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
