      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫SNR</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4DHS9fibU6e1bYfBxm2AF7_2VS_GeyiW6kXpvJnU9KQsUHTOp2yZdPpqKLE631iZO6_-yPagr3XfL7UjKAD0qx3GRD_mCeVZAPJ-dXAeuXRJkFzx0mp1Vo8yoMYrrqslU_HmbG9Opd8cIbIOVj1MiRpU9T4CLm4X7vlu8XpOC2f1JzbGw6PJt1tBPAadz7vb9PAL4?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Southwark, Peckham SE15<br><br>SNR (Show No Remorse) are a small street gang based around Leyton Square and the Friary estate in Peckham, within the SE15 postcode. They beef with Ghetto, Silwood, Moscow17, Browning17 and AY17.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2801-117</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
