        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Lewisham SE13<br><br>O'Lanna are a small street gang based on the Lethbridge estate between Lewisham and Deptford, within the SE13 postcode. They are loosely allied with Ghetto and Block 6,  whilst they beef M20, SG and BSide.<br><br>Associated Rappers} 3 O'Lanna / 6 O'Lanna / 7 O'Lanna / 8 O'Lanna]]></description>
