      <Placemark>
        <name>GP</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Lewisham SE13<br><br>GP (Grab Peez) are a street gang from Lewisham, within the SE13 postcode.  The gang are mostly active on the Cornmill Gardens estate, known locally as "New Park", which is a new build estate on the site of the old Sundermead estate, which was demolished in the mid 2000s. GP are also active on the Coldbath Street estate.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Bookey / Lockz / Smokey / Skizz]]></description>
