        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4oAiSxl0LYly65NhOmwneQl14Soyexg4eQCEnDowz4zvE7c_jH-mXL15Ut4QZd5xO7QY3bbAHhlynNctDGjUEVLaJW8f1s5XNyhGi_hBwbJVfa_jN5T-v803klCfWvL34YtPMb1aKcj1eXO3dUxNEqIa2LNU2anTSZ069OOlYXMa2LCli7UIoNEGBv7MknTHH1nAI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Waddon CR0<br><br>Waddon are street gang based on the Duppas Hill estate in the Waddon area of Croydon, within the CR0 postcode. The gang identify with the colour blue. They OLane.<br><br>Associated Rappers} KMulla]]></description>
