        <name>🔵Dorset Road

https://web.archive.org/web/20120206081321/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/south-london-gangs/crips-cripset</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4hbE_ttK8S1SN2rhzIgfKWVNi_ndelwkfyZ_2acFjbnRMt-O4qiJig--2nsJzBxjwvyvgcsuYkk1upMmokw5_qzfKhLBUzxIUvJHIt1ELvhZIUUmw0Nsg2E1s1UklGvvFi1ZG7GvgEpIhrK62A7t4R-Zx4-rOl7_ZdDqScoXe7eQXh0WtGLW7Px_78ypAryt0vTHs?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lambeth, South Lambeth SW8<br><br>'Dorset Road' are a set who are located around Dorset Road on the South Lambeth and Mursell estates, which are in the South Lambeth area between Vauxhall and Stockwell within the SW8 postcode. The set were part of the Cripset alliance around 2006-2008/09, which was a linkup of ALC, MZ, ABM, Dorset Road and Claptown. They were known for their fierce rivalry with nearby 031 Bloods. By 2009/10 the 'Dorset Road Crips' had died out and their territory was then taken over by the larger '031' Bloods and a set known as the 'Killa Gangsta Bloods' (KGB). They had affiliations with Croydon (Byrdgang and KGB). ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-2201-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
