      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Harlem</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5lyzLN36uufTsa7OwSWe6tHMY9KiZ3HdHRdMdqgkS1RhkId91hgOG3h_qWPANo4RTyx8IdJXaUFQGSXgtutsrHOH392vsIMK9J0ja8OcflULz7Zs9GlkLpM6HRg6f9WlQih6tFW8wUyKQNcUI6gNTeTEwVK3r1CEd_1XVk6NgHCQDQk28avr9XMN75b3bOEKPo2pw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Lambeth, Kennington SE11<br><br>Harlem are a large street gang from Kennington particularly Kennington Park, Penwith Manor and Kennings estates, but they draw membership from the wider Kennington area. The gang are also referred to as 'Harlem Spartans' (HS) and also HarlemO (HarlemOnly). The area of Kennington is known as 'Harlem' which is where the gang get their name. They are a relatively new gang only forming in the mid 2010s. They are a new younger Kennington generation to Black Prince/BYM (Bang Your Mash) who had been active from the mid 2000s to early 2010s. Before this the Kennington Park/KP set were more aligned with OC from nearby Myatts Field, who are the olders of 410, and had beef with Black Prince/BYM. Harlem allied with nearby KuKu, Moscow17, Browning17, AY17, 674 and SIRU, whilst they beef with nearby 410, 150, 17, 031, 37, 061, Uptop, Claptown, Zone 2, YPB, CMB and China Walk.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Loski / Mizormac / TG Millian / Blanco / Bis / Zico / OnDrills / Trapfit / Scratcha / H1 / Jmash / Lil S]]></description>
