      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵SBV / SBlock / LPW</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5Yfq5J1cQC_5uw-TEhTGRmtdWbdG0XnPQ6TPohKiw2W0q4zkv9bFkGcBOVO120Qn51g7Y35YUN2HBcbZQnNEqWAJGpxzd7voYeCrRqrKSnVoEFPNY6Xbt-EBObSTrBB5Ftqkkupa2Ihx_aSbaXiwuTjQPC90SqhJlzopA5dN3cVeBkd0cs1krE77cEkJ1FPsXh55NNQlGOsNoPXjShuHIkNjNNc0tw_Z--ZVGvkbyYH1GN?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Croydon, Croydon SE25/CR0<br><br>SBV / SBlock are a small gang based around Selhurst and Croydon, within the SE25 and CR0 postcodes. The set are most active on the small estates such as around Selhurst Place, Selhurst New Road and Cromwell Road. SBV stand for 'SinBlockVillains' and 'SelhurstBlockVillains'. They are part of the LPW (Little Patch World) alliance who identify with the colour blue. They are allied with 5th, VP, STK and CR7. They beef with CR0 and Fieldway.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Handy / LK / Amz]]></description>
