      <Placemark>
        <name>KWO / 25 / RG</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Croydon, South Norwood SE25<br><br>25 are a street gang who are based around South Norwood, within the SE25 postcode. They are most active on the small estates around South Norwood such as those based around Stockbury Road and Longheath Gardens. They beef STK, 5th and SBV.<br><br>Associated Members} Trapx10 / Juggx10 / DRose / Limma / S'Kizzy / KyKy ]]></description>
