      <Placemark>
        <name>KWO</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Croydon, South Norwood SE25/CR0<br><br>KWO (Kelva's World Only) are a small set based around the South Norwood and Croydon area, within the SE25 and CR0 postcodes. They are most active around Sunnybank, Portland Road, Davidson Road, Moreland Road and Christie Drive. They are allied with CR0 and Fieldway. They beef with SBV, CR7 and SplashSet.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Jugg247 ]]></description>
