        <name>🟢NGB / North Greenwich / G-Town</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Greenwich, North Greenwich SE10<br><br>NGB (North Greenwich Boys), also known as 'G-Town', are a small set who are based in the North Greenwich area. They are allied with 10Side, H-Block, Cherry and SRoad. They have beef with WoolyO, Wildbatch and GS28.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Culprit / JB]]></description>
