      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢CMB / 500</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4jfZ5L2cyxGvY55Zqi67ICAl1CCev7OdfHRi0zJc4cBTeaQ9KzfXlw-aDlj90MKLGMJg9q3D-W2qAqq1DIitAilWU7YjYM4_B_vexPIzQJLrmZMtxIiDsP95xwb0-IdMLiCKRiNxRvIQPkOj-DVrQp-W2ENyiuad1jQjpkViQZRpO2axoCoSOFGvsBHGDpadpzgaCYToiJ5u2o09rP8i60wxQrVwFWeeWQiMoHRuaf4_6K?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Southwark, Camberwell SE5<br><br>CMB/500 are a street gang based around Camberwell Road on the Elmington and the Wyndham estates in Camberwell, within the SE5 postcode. CMB/500 are allied with 150, 410, Claptown and Uptop. They beef with Moscow17, Browning17, AY17, Harlem, KuKu, 674, LTH and ABM.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Trapfit / Tapeoff / 5hunna / Kayos500 / HB / T Splash]]></description>
