        <name>🔘YCB</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Deptford SE8<br><br>YCB are a small set who are based on the Crossfields estate in Deptford, within the SE8 postcode. The identify with the colour grey. They are allied with WildBatch and Ghetto. They beef with ARB, H-Block, Cherry and WoolyO.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Jiggz / LJ / Squeezo / Jetz / CS]]></description>
