      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢⚫ARB / 10Side / TenSide / OG10</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Greenwich, East Greenwich SE10<br><br>ARB (Armitage Road Boys) are a street gang based around Armitage Road on the on the Flamsteed and Caletock estates in East Greenwich, within the SE10 postcode. They are also known as '10Side'. They are allied with H-Block, Cherry and SRoad. They have beef with CHG, AWB, WildBatch and WoolyO.<br><br>Associated Rappers} T10 / Kemz / Izzo / Lk / Lz]]></description>
