      <Placemark>
        <name>NDO / 27</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lambeth, West Norwood SE27<br><br>NDO (No Days Off) are a small street gang based on the Hainthorpe and Dunbar & Dunelm estates in West Norwood, within the SE27 postcode. They are mostly a trapping set. They tend to be allied with Claptown, 17, 37, 150, 410, UTH and Croydon sets, such as LPW, STK, SBV, VP and 730. They beef CP, T1D, Gipset, 67, LTH, ABM, 55 and Harlem.<br><br>Associated Rappers} K Rose / Siru ]]></description>
