        <name>Crofton Park / CP</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lewisham, Brockley SE4<br><br>CP are a small street gang based in the Crofton Park area of Brockley, within the SE4 postcode. They are mostly made up of ex-BSide and ex-26 members. They beef Harlem, M20, 26, BSide and LDG/BlueHillz.]]></description>
