        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Lambeth, West Norwood SW16/SE27<br><br>Crown Point (CP) are a small street gang based on the Fern Lodge and Holderness estates in West Norwood, within the SE27 postcode. They are a fairly new set who used to be a trapping set, but have recently also started getting into beef. They tend to be allied with Gipsy Hill, 674, 55, LTH, BG, 417, SWC, 25s, Mitcham and Pollards. They beef NDO, Uptop, CR7, GLane, LPW, M20, SIRU, 150, 410, 17 and 37.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Main Road  36 / GLA]]></description>
