      <Placemark>
        <name>84 / YCG / KrashTown</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Greenwich, Gallions Hill, West Thamesmead SE28<br><br>84, formerly known as YCG and KrashTown are a small street gang based in the Gallions Hill area of the larger West Thamesmead area in the Borough of Greenwich, within the SE28 postcode. Another street gang in this area are MDrive, based predominately around the Miles Drive estate. They beef with NGB, OG10, CHG and YDB.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Stizz / Deefigs / LJ / Dottz / Karma / SY (MDrive)]]></description>
