      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵A9 / Hirst Crescent (HC)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5uy0pXHPVMK56ZOH6V1fUW8J2UbviAPG68G-RzKsKCLB7P72_4PHKLNWjBlsBH9l0ssF5IY9DoXTZ9aTTe_01q3swK21QdKIen_qDNMmjgTjh0T_WkwDWxVqOw6JePqEAJxDaL2aNhuvMTeLMRSiVwhtldEi8rzMkl2Ia2RCxQKHKMbQBIzf5HZEmZ12LiDykIVE0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Brent, Wembley HA9<br><br>A9 are a street gang who are based on the Hirst Crescent estate and the Chalkhill estate in Wembley within the HA9 postcode. They are also known as the 'HC Boyz' (HC) and identify with the colour blue. They are allied with Chalkhill, Stonebridge, South Kilburn and Monks Park.  A9 beef with Press Road, Kingsbury and Wembley Fornia Dons but also have conflict with Church Road, Kensal Green and Mozart.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-2801-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5uy0pXHPVMK56ZOH6V1fUW8J2UbviAPG68G-RzKsKCLB7P72_4PHKLNWjBlsBH9l0ssF5IY9DoXTZ9aTTe_01q3swK21QdKIen_qDNMmjgTjh0T_WkwDWxVqOw6JePqEAJxDaL2aNhuvMTeLMRSiVwhtldEi8rzMkl2Ia2RCxQKHKMbQBIzf5HZEmZ12LiDykIVE0?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
