      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫D-Block (DBG)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Barnet, Burnt Oak HA8<br><br>D-Block are a street gang based around Deansbrook Road in the Burnt Oak area of Edgware, within the HA8 postcode and they also have links to Grahame Park estate, within the NW9 postcode. They are predominantly of Somali origin and they are allied with Thug Fam, also a predominantly Somali gang, based on the nearby Grahame Park estate.  They have been known to come into conflict with Finchley.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2401-77</styleUrl>
        <Polygon>
          <outerBoundaryIs>
            <LinearRing>
