      <Placemark>
        <name>Cromer Street Massive

https://web.archive.org/web/20110417004511/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/northwest-london-gangs/cromer-street-massive-cromer-street-posse</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Camden, St Pancras WC1<br><br>Cromer Street Massive are a Bengali gang based around Cromer Street in the St Pancras and Kings Cross areas. Their main rivals are the nearby Drummond Street Posse.]]></description>
