      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Active Gxng (AG / AGB)

https://web.archive.org/web/20110529200320/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/northwest-london-gangs/centric-crew</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4cgVqVV1lXc18ToqjE4rOVQu_-2RDmIh12kK4ebrqvDXLZag6-1wX-Xu7FomRSC8fhnhpQMMmBgy8LqaF37h361bP3LKc-6KfZnhESQFqIxep5vS3MRSpDZsjnWR-xaV-C7D1ds4FdgPp5o7Dl9Ry2MXV9WWYKCddhLFI2cVVNbmvTavqTHgy0s0TxOI8FKGZYEvz_ZhOgIkMzr6P_fBGR7pKViAAuIu0XW5E5ZgrdXVOq?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Camden, Camden Town NW1<br><br>Active Gxng (AG) are a street gang who are based on the Agar Grove, Maiden Lane and St Pancras Way estates in Camden, within the NW1 postcode, known locally as 'Crack 1st'. They are known as AG (Agar Grove / Active Gxng) and AGB (Active Gxng Boys / Agar Grove Boys).<br><br>They are a predominantly Somali gang although not all members are necessarily Somali. Camden has a long history of Somali gangs and AG have grown during the 2010s to become the dominant Somali gang in Camden following on from older sets such as 'Centric' and 'TMS'. They identify with the colour red and are often referred to as 'Bloods'. Much of their hood has been demolished and rebuilt during the 2010s and has undergone an extensive regeneration project. Their main block is Lulworth Tower which is a tower block on the Agar Grove estate which dominates the areas skyline which has remained despite the surrounding area being demolished and rebuilt. The tower has featured regularly in music videos and album covers from the gangs rappers.  <br><br>They are allied with 'FSG', 'CT1' and 'NRB' in an alliance known as '71st' after the N7 and NW1 postcodes where the sets are based. They also have links with 'Mozart' and 'A-Team'. Their main rivals are 'Cumbo', 'Peckwater' and 'Queens Crescent' who form an alliance known as '51st' after the NW5 and NW1 postcodes where they are based.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Suspect / Broadday / Strika / T Scam / 2Smokey / SWavey / Yevz]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2701-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4cgVqVV1lXc18ToqjE4rOVQu_-2RDmIh12kK4ebrqvDXLZag6-1wX-Xu7FomRSC8fhnhpQMMmBgy8LqaF37h361bP3LKc-6KfZnhESQFqIxep5vS3MRSpDZsjnWR-xaV-C7D1ds4FdgPp5o7Dl9Ry2MXV9WWYKCddhLFI2cVVNbmvTavqTHgy0s0TxOI8FKGZYEvz_ZhOgIkMzr6P_fBGR7pKViAAuIu0XW5E5ZgrdXVOq?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
