      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴Wembley Fornia Dons (WFD)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7evE9mhq5S5UkZU0sZ3WQ-Iy8cOLuWEKBCQcVJEcjcr5SpQ9MdvjOGQ0ypDDa7qbE4WGPrkvY90uiybbth2Eti80EA05ELYuWhmMwuGfSV-XoAA5vBR1_sIjknIsQWJ8ffzYotgmr7kdAq-6JdbphCunaiNPHqjqKvwBXXuzcv5HTWvQtZkRc9T-BwDKR4dYaM2do?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Brent, Wembley HA9<br><br>Wembley Fornia Dons (WFD) are a large street gang who are from Wembley. They are based on a number of small estates around Lancelot Road and Wembley High Road, including the Barley Close, Milford Gardens and King George Gardens area estates. They formed around 2007 and were part of the STA9 group who also had members from areas including Neasden, Kilburn and Cricklewood. They are allied with the Press Road, St Raphs, Kingsbury, Kensal Green, Mozart and North Kilburn areas.  They beef with Chalkhill, A9, Monks Park, Stonebridge and South Kilburn.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2801-117</styleUrl>
