      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Wealdstone (SCG)

https://web.archive.org/web/20111231210520/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/northwest-london-gangs/wealdstone-black-gang-wbg</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6CiBV9sAeTQx7qXwbH02L-bF0qe_yEEwpc8lJokPesQaf6pT015NzwbvEmN_8o6G1vRSlDEUjRYOurG2KSlsCOWJvOaw5TcZh6e2ojN07P9hngdFnUMjNmfU-5n4WSQ2n5DiRqjxTPYSCUjK9xDOqkVksGDLMhCpL-u7MllBbN6nH43d7b3gk_QiEtiy6jJFBS4NU?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Harrow, Wealdstone HA3<br><br>The 'Wealdstone Black Gang' are a small street gang based in the Wealdstone area of Harrow. The gang are also known as SCG (Stay Certified Goons/Stone City Goons).  The gang were briefly known as 'Grey Gang' in 2007, before opting for the colour black. Much of the gang are from North and East African countries, predominantly Somalia. Harrow is one of the safest and least deprived areas of London known for its wealthy suburban, and sometimes village like, communities. Their main area of gang activity is around Wealdstone High Street, Peel Road and Cumberland Court. Naturally with few nearby rivals 'Rayners Lane' from South Harrow became the main rivals to Wealdstone area. The current generation from Wealdstone are allied with former rivals Rayners Lane. They beef with Queensbury, Northolt, Greenford and Southall.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2501-122</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6CiBV9sAeTQx7qXwbH02L-bF0qe_yEEwpc8lJokPesQaf6pT015NzwbvEmN_8o6G1vRSlDEUjRYOurG2KSlsCOWJvOaw5TcZh6e2ojN07P9hngdFnUMjNmfU-5n4WSQ2n5DiRqjxTPYSCUjK9xDOqkVksGDLMhCpL-u7MllBbN6nH43d7b3gk_QiEtiy6jJFBS4NU?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
