      <Placemark>
        <name>Swiss Cottage / L-Block</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Camden, Swiss Cottage NW3/NW6<br><br>The Swiss Cottage sets are based on the Rowley Way estate, and also around the Lithos Road and Dresden Close estates, covering the NW3/NW6/NW8 postcodes.  Swiss Cottage are also known as 'Sin City'. One well known older Swiss Cottage set are known as ASA (Angry Streets Army) who are based on the Rowley Way estate, having been formed in the Paddington recreation centre before moving to Rowley Way. Another main set 'L-Block' are based around Lithos Road and Dresden Close estates. Swiss Cottage are allied with the North Kilburn, STA9 and Cricklewood gangs. They beef with Queens Crescent and Lisson Green.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2501-77</styleUrl>
