      <Placemark>
        <name>Queensbury (QB)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Harrow, Queensbury HA3/HA8<br><br>Queensbury (QB) are a small street gang based around the Mollison Way in the Queensbury area of Harrow. They beef with Wealdstone, Rayners Lane, Cricklewood and Finchley.]]></description>
