      <Placemark>
        <name>Cricklewood / CWood / 2Side</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Barnet, Cricklewood NW2<br><br>2Side are a small street gang who are based in Cricklewood area, known as 'CWood', within the NW2 postcode. They are most active on the Clitterhouse estate near the Brent Cross area. They are allied with Swiss Cottage. Their main rivalry is with Lisson Green.<br><br>Associated Rappers} JaySav / Chuckz / Double R]]></description>
