      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵Peckwater</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X69FhS5dc_TOGnfa3MKAVT_KX0BjDNwVu1KX1-iK5Ie2UBm0LPc1gDkO7Y4OrPZvt36KsKuJI759TGbq_CRcnR-r1SprHKDubk3kTP5Vm1oThLmM8ouf2h1237QqvKLWrZii50CWCQxJaU10kEJdvU2c0eTl9VSgzNuBhfsf9f28pCUXCdrDBTo9q0M80c6Wwbq-GE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Camden, Kentish Town NW5<br><br>Peckwater, often known as "Waterz", are a street gang who are located on the Peckwater estate and some surrounding blocks in the Kentish Town area of Camden, within the NW5 postcode, known locally as 'Crack 5th'.<br><br>In the past the Peckwater estate was less active with many gang members from their area identifying more with nearby Queens Crescent, which has been a longer established area and gang for many decades. The current generation started to form during the mid 2010s, and although many of the set members don't necessarily live on the estate they are one of the most active sets in Camden. Their gang identify with the colour of blue and many of the gang are of Congolese origin much like their closest allies of Cumbo. Some of the current generation form a set known as OS (One Side).<br><br>They are allied with 'Cumbo' and 'Queens Crescent' in an alliance known as '51st' after the NW5 and NW1 postcodes where they are situated. Their main rivals are 'Active Gxng', 'FSG', 'CT1' and 'NRB' who form an alliance known as '71st' after the N7 and NW1 postcodes where they are based.<br><br>Associated Rappers} C2 / Action / Lankz / Wandz]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-2501-77</styleUrl>
