      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Rayners Lane (RL)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X51zQRqz5fEKrOgSHx6HjAD_LooevPrSJVB-MjWVH7W3d-2ZSFrjl2VvLZqOfTCdXmKsXHIIGZEHTcyjkjpKHksvKSyDS_Q4bGVs_V5MsNeeal01L_5kXvv9BujIJJEQrmgugbFgEIWx0pCovO7k-iTSc7wLLSeK_-OzSL03Z9YYmCmQc480aiEs_yvgDrfZ8l4gTs?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Harrow, South Harrow HA2<br><br>Rayners Lane (RL) are a large street gang who are located on the Rayners Lane and Apple Grove estates and around nearby Kings Road in South Harrow, within the HA2 postcode. RL are also known as FLB (Fast Lane Boys). RL are allied with former rivals in Wealdstone and 9th Street as well as Ladbroke Grove and Hayes. They beef Northolt, Greenford and Southall.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Breezo / Sizz / Risky / Teerose]]></description>
