      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴YHB</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6o3A1IyvzOVtXTvW6Fe9W2WU6bBgce_zXjUI3VmewYZJ123MIW57DPXgAa4F38NPHe1dY_-Se0DKyXzQiG360gzueUslxsTCIfEEAgLzstEbd6sRWsMHz40vddj3hz_aRSAjjtl0GfUrQehwT_7MOOXN6YOOS4PCpxeamB-qiqTlu88V-S9hdnfg-AVyt7yIYMjaSyaPoW75VHm5DFemG4AQYFzLeMvgq2Zz1e-oKbBxFx?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Brent, Harlesden NW10<br><br>YHB (Young Harlesden Boys) are a set who are based around Harlesden, within the NW10 postcode. They are mostly active on the Marian Way and Roundwood estates. They are a Blood gang and identify with the colour red.  They are affiliated with Church Road who they share much of their territory with. They beef Stonebridge, South Kilburn, Monks Park and Chalkhill.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Rooga]]></description>
