      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫🔴NSB / MGM</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Brent, Stonebridge NW10<br><br>Northside Bizzy (NSB) are a small set who are based on the northside of Stonebridge estate, within the NW10 postcode. northside gang also went by MGM (Machine Gun Murderers) during the late 2000s to mid 2010s. During this period there was in house beef in Stonebridge, which for a while resulted in members from the northside of Stonebridge beefing their Stonebridge members from the southside. It's calmed down now,  but there are still tensions between certain individuals. At one point northside Stonebridge aligned themselves more with Stonebridges main rivals St Raphs and Church Road but they are now more cliqued up with the rest of Stonebridge as well as their allies in South Kilburn, Chalkhill and Monks Park. They have beef with St Raphs, Church Road and Mozart. ]]></description>
