      <Placemark>
        <name>Page Street / Paid Block</name>
        <description><![CDATA[City of Westminster, Pimlico SW1<br><br>Page Street are a small street gang based around Page Street on the Regency and Millbank estates in the Pimlico area, known as ‘Pimz Town’. They refer to their block are "Paid Block". The gang beef with the Church Town Militants and Ebury Town Militants. They have ties to gangs in Lambeth.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Bishop]]></description>
