        <name>143 / Feltham</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hounslow, Feltham TW13/TW14<br><br>143 are a street gang based in the Feltham area of Hounslow, within the TW13/TW14 postcodes. They are allied with their offshoot SBlock and Butts Farm. They beef with 7Side and CCLanerz.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Kayz / Melly / Tee / SA / AJ]]></description>
