re splitting into new sets, which included '12Anti', '12World' '1200' and '8712'. The current sets are most active around the White City, Cleverly, Becklow Gardens and Emlyn Gardens estates in Shepherds Bush W12 and also the Friary Park and Trinity Way estates in Acton W3. They identify with the colour red to oppose rivals from the nearby South Acton and Ladbroke Grove areas who identify with the colour blue. The largest, and most well known, of these current sets are '12Anti' (12A). The current sets are affiliated with Hounslow, Northolt, Greenford and Southall, whilst their main rivalry is with Ladbroke Grove, although they also beef nearby South Acton, Hayes and West Drayton.<br><br>Associated Rappers} BOX12 / A2Anti / Fdot / Sav12 / Ryder / Little Katty]]></description>
