        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X46JQpGg3vdGw9wd0jpcb2pRnBa0JcBiovIjSwfPceQhirrsgG864jNK9KvB1j-FRcT6A8p-y0aiNnyqvquLW5lPy7PuYHu6Qn_Vm_bMlIS1KoFtQaP76CT8l_Uxu_fwATvgCVcOyMKZrWXYYcGgUBZ3s8e_6hQQmNXzzaE8N7elZ6Tl3VcZ1Nq86v3L-GDq__mFvZe?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Royal Borough of Kensington & Chelsea, Ladbroke Grove W10<br><br>Golborne are a street gang located around Golborne Road and the Kensal Town area of North Kensington, within the W10 postcode.]]></description>
