      <Placemark>
        <name>7Side / SWR</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hounslow, Isleworth TW7<br><br>7Side are a street gang from the Isleworth area, within the TW7 postcode near Twickenham Rugby stadium. They are also known as 'SWR'. They beef 143/Feltham, ERoad, Butts Farm, CCLanerz, Oriel/TW13, Section 8, 54z and South Acton.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Mitch'O / Hunna / Shakk / DBoy / Kamz / Kapo / Krasha]]></description>
