      <Placemark>
        <name>🟣Purple Hayes / 3rdSide</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6f_3lgy3YVTdPv9U5bjyKAlRz_KkzA4aCcNZ2dHsS--A5dNGhzpbZC0XNWQ_ChaDgnqtIsi6D-YkKcpFhzPddWACLDDGH2PQfxHLNDU7PCWiA8AWb3naADMlw-PAlbiv0ji4q0ykSS4Zbdg4Kh8wAIp2z5eq0GGuLD0WjEiVbmeRq8zkZr68ele-pmUjlgESHHbLg?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hillingdon, Hayes UB3<br><br>Purple Hayes (PH) are based in Addison Way, Avondale Drive and St Chrstopher's Drive in Hayes, within the UB3 postcode. They are also known as Section 18 (S18) and Bully Unit (BU). Hayes are allied with nearby West Drayton and Rayners Lane.  They beef Shepherds Bush, Southall, Northolt, Greenford and South Acton.]]></description>
