        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X61nUCDx35pGaSLEm7CXAhIqbnXT6ucIW20WLOoK6uDeL9nAu2cBJBQQcSJbCh2DNx1XTwXnmyPGlWNlUL72YOEcgiHFHjPclMNzuJbFw7h6WbfhaGKUIa_EODxj505BT2nOAU4Oz8QkRgZqfxKV4Rp4nrAExcaWRvsQHcNDVn3GuygJeXCb9ljiuCXHM3iHc1VXKM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hounslow, Brentford TW8<br><br>Section 8 are based on the Green Dragon estate in the Brentford area of Hounslow, within the TW8 postcode. They are allied with 54z. They beef with 7Side.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Millz / JC / Teyzer]]></description>
