      <Placemark>
        <name>Butts Farm / WL / Winners Lane</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hounslow, Hanworth TW13<br><br>WL (Winners Lane) are a street gang based on the Butts Farm estate and nearby Butts Crescent area in the Hanworth area of Hounslow, within the TW13 postcode. Butts Farm are allied with 143/Feltham and Shepherds Bush. They beef with ERoad and 7Side.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Katman]]></description>
