      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵54z</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7lJojEe0eUANIqghEPi9yDNPTCnp_8yRhp6R7D6SBnsuPPjGbfDE7ovpMBe7MCHnR-xEoXC48PptdocHw-6W4dwebPsSMvKe52izLIYkfsHApz-VfNWpLpGcs1dcBAOenDj1dbgopwm6bMkApLzQZKp4o0OsLi6TY9SpheZ1t6H7WdfhaTdevI9-R7aM07wZKNY1Y?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hounslow, South Ealing W5<br><br>54z are a street gang based on the Clayponds estate in South Ealing on the borders of both Ealing and Hownslow boroughs, within the W5 postcode. They are also active on some nearby estates, such as Watchfield, Sutton Lane, Horticultural and St Thomas Road estates, within the W4 postcode. The name of '54z' comes from the 'W5' and 'W4' postcodes. They are allied with South Acton and Section 8. They beef with 7Side.]]></description>
