      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴WK£ </name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6I2_xBRVKzsZown35yspy-YqyjhBHp5MNy4qRlF9F-mpcwsy6MG1fEsYZlDY4ql5HCdnO9ArEEvPWJ-yiimVA5T1uCeT1VFk3KoxRAW2K3eZxLRpnaO_D338ehCwfJOxGBrCvWPl1l3jsdmKKrrvG7mXY_Hyn9CFIGpmxT3-NCfKA3HECcUArzFbsBYzN5wuwyw2MG?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hammersmith & Fulham, Fulham and West Kensington SW6<br><br>WK£ (North End Road) are a street gang based around North End Road located around Fulham, West Kensington and West Brompton, within the SW6 postcode. They are situated on the West Kensington, Clem Atlee Court, Lancaster Court, Fulham Court and Bayonne Park estates. They identify with the colour red and are closely allied with '12Anti' (Shepherds Bush) and can be considered a set of '12Anti'. They also have links with QCR. They beef Worlds End, S£B and IPL.<br><br>Associated Rappers} TR2]]></description>
