        <name>IPL</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hammersmith & Fulham, Hurlingham SW6<br><br>IPL are a small set based on the Pearscroft and Imperial Wharf estates in the Fulham area, within the SW6 postcode. They are allied with S£B and beef with WK£.]]></description>
