        <name>🔵 G-Road</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hammersmith & Fulham, Shepherd's Bush W12<br><br>G-Road are a small set who are based on the small estates around Goldhawk Road in Shepherds Bush, within the W12 postcode. The set used to be known as 'Stay Banging' (SB).<br><br>Associated Rappers} Don Tanch]]></description>
