      <name>North London</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Red Brick / Deadmonton</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N18<br><br>Red Brick Thugs, also known as the Red Brick Crew, are a street gang based on the Klinger estate, which is situated along Silver Street in Edmonton, within the N18 postcode. They are known as 'Red Brick' as the Klinger estate where they are based is made up of red bricks. They are allies to Edmonton Grey Gang and EvaStrap from Tottenham. They  are known for their beef with the Dem Africans gang from Edmonton (N9) during the late 2000s and the early 2010s. The current younger generation from the Upper Edmonton area, situated within the N18 postcode, are now known as 'Deadmonton' who are most active around the Fore Street area, Scott House and Beck House.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-A52714-2601-77</styleUrl>
