      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴SOS / GMF

https://web.archive.org/web/20110625104942/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/north-london-gangs/shakespeare-sos-soldiers-of-shakespeare</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7U1Dixr2-78U9Wc54Cf_E9ct7MOBR652PZodoH5E6zarOKW46bb22-kkN48-MuuJgPL7qCu5VRLE3yw_uaEsEZG5eX2iZYsN0H9udaf46SdlLrDF_5HYPgRLpzshPALarXX6JswjSpDOIwQlYuo--FrX1DXLA8QYiIZ-uN8Eie0dGq1JsXocVTCybBIaqcyPGEnfQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hackney, Stoke Newington N16<br><br>The Soldiers of Shakespeare are a street gang based on the Milton Gardens estate although also have influence over the nearby Mayville, Mildmay and Shellgrove estates, situated in the Stoke Newington area in the north of Hackney within the N16 postcode. The gang take their name from 'Shakespeare Walk', a street running through the Milton Gardens estate.<br><br>The 'Shakespeare' gang was formed in the latter half of the 1990s. Today they are commonly known by the acronym of SOS (Soldiers Of Shakespeare or Shoot On Sight). Some of the original members of the gang were part of the Hackney 'Rowdy Bunch', and remained close to the Holly Street Boys section of 'Rowdy Bunch'. The gang are also closely aligned with nearby 'Red Pitch'. Some of the Shakespeare gang had also doubled up as generals for the newer 'Red Pitch' Gang. Historically they are known for rivalry with Stoke Newington (Lordship, Smalley and Rectory).<br><br>Historically they have been allied with Red Pitch and Holly Street. Soldiers of Shakespeare had been known to come into conflict with Stoke Newington, Fellows Court, Hoxton, Essex Road, A-Road, Cally Road, Pembury, Homerton and Hindle House.<br><br>The current younger generations are known as GMF (Get Money Fast). They are allied with Holly Street, Homerton, Pembury, Essex Road, Hoxton and Kingshold.  They beef London Fields, Stoke Newington, A-Road, Mountford and Fellows Court. <br><br>Associated Rappers} Smokes GMF]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2701-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7U1Dixr2-78U9Wc54Cf_E9ct7MOBR652PZodoH5E6zarOKW46bb22-kkN48-MuuJgPL7qCu5VRLE3yw_uaEsEZG5eX2iZYsN0H9udaf46SdlLrDF_5HYPgRLpzshPALarXX6JswjSpDOIwQlYuo--FrX1DXLA8QYiIZ-uN8Eie0dGq1JsXocVTCybBIaqcyPGEnfQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
