      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢GLane / 48</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6K5h4TF3NcRA78WRRwd7L7MkH6LOwQpkNtXm4SxcoeyenrTLdgfeJjf9qUcYPsaIMGy9J32vL39ZRMqhcy_GwmMrQ7d0jVztejMvsBTMaLxlOx8KZE55_CTFyhRdGQsS4buUaIrU0Clw9w3ck3gsh-urRrebLENGj2NdY6uT4DLqjtxqXarTdKWHLarhAvNCzrXyE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Haringey, Harringay N4<br><br>'G Lane', also known as '48' and '400', are a small street gang from the Green Lanes area around Finsbury Park Avenue and Carlton Road, within the N4 postcode. They beef the N15 and Tiverton gangs from the South Tottenham area.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-558B2F-2801-77</styleUrl>
