        <name>🔴De Beauvoir</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6Cvq1R19Ykw0rcANfuMKPdCZQb20bptg7ktZ2cYFerLREYF4omDt5gx7BUGdYUJORxq2BpZh0gaoMyt7RxmaZ16zH1fW-4_kaeK2IkPBvKA4h5uMz5xF0BUDAbzPkNYDRRozd4v6gKix4OSU_uiaF3pNvilLJHymFGtR6KSsh0LpjSO2DqdSdCk0Xv4iCS2uTJ3Fdi?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hackney, De Beauvoir Town N1<br><br>De Beauvoir are a small street gang who are based on the De Beauvoir estate in Hackney, within the N1 postcode, situated on the border of Hackney and Islington boroughs. The estate is affiliated with the Hoxton, Holly Street and Homerton areas.<br><br>Associated Rappers} NSG (Rap collective from the area)]]></description>
