      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴N15

https://web.archive.org/web/20110719171523/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/north-london-gangs/ida-rydaz-ida-bloodstarz</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6qfP5qk-Sv50QrAL-OkyeRrV-mGKEdWP3M_0IsCbdj18jkXnhI70xwRuAWCSYZeWkrHH3dh-Hf6YeECA5eTLq6xXdZsvEbfkQkuGjCxo4WuWL1Fm7z1NDnhBSwgV3Q9hWxOCOvHG3lwEZuoq-LECrjpZmftcpRuQ8R6rjEk0LuhpNso1Duz7c8VXBJU9oF-FJh5_I?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Haringey, South Tottenham N15<br><br>N15 set are based on the Edgecot Grove, Appleby Close, Ida Road and Stonebridge estates in the South Tottenham area, within the N15 postcode. The gang formed around 2003/04 when the 'Tottenham Mandem' (TMD) group began to break up into a number of the smaller estate based sets, and later independent gangs, active across Tottenham N15/N17 that we see today. Originally the group were known as 'Ida Boyz' or the 'Ida Rydaz' before they adopted the identity of Bloods during the mid 2000s and would go on to become known as the 'Ida Bloodstarz'. The current younger generation of gang members from the area are known simply as 'N15'. They are allied with Tiverton and OFB. They beef Wood Green/N22, Edmonton/N9, GLane, TPL/DC8, TPL/OTP and former allies NPK.<br><br>Associated Rappers} K1 / D Rose]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2701-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6qfP5qk-Sv50QrAL-OkyeRrV-mGKEdWP3M_0IsCbdj18jkXnhI70xwRuAWCSYZeWkrHH3dh-Hf6YeECA5eTLq6xXdZsvEbfkQkuGjCxo4WuWL1Fm7z1NDnhBSwgV3Q9hWxOCOvHG3lwEZuoq-LECrjpZmftcpRuQ8R6rjEk0LuhpNso1Duz7c8VXBJU9oF-FJh5_I?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
