      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴⚫Ferry Lane / GMR</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Haringey, Tottenham N17<br><br>GMR are a street gang who are located on the Ferry Lane estate and around the Tottenham Hale area of Tottenham, within the N17 postcode. The older generation from Ferry Lane have been referred to as "Ferry Lane Bloods", or also "Bloodline". GMR are allied with ChingHall. They beef with Selrack/ARG.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Tkash / Jmash / Patz / Whyem / YS / YC / TB / HC]]></description>
