        <name>P-Block / Ponders / 83</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Ponders End EN3<br><br>P-Block are a small street gang based on the Alma Road estate in the Ponders End area of Enfield, within the EN3 postcode.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Jayzo / JDM / TMG]]></description>
