      <Placemark>
        <name>🟠EnnyTown</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Enfield EN2<br><br>EnnyTown are a street gang who are based around Enfield Town, particularly in the Lavender Hill area, within the EN2 postcode. They identify with the colour of orange. They are allied with GMG/AP. They beef Edmonton.<br><br>Associated Rappers} N2Savv'0 / Reekaa / M2]]></description>
