      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢1T / OneTray</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Palmers Green N13<br><br>1T (OneTray) are a street gang who are based in the Palmers Green area, within the N13 postcode. Historically 1T had also been known as 'P-Town', or 'P-Block'. The gang are allied with TPL/OTP and Wood Green/N22. They beef the TPL/DC8 and Hornsey/V8 gangs.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Rambizz / Hizzy13 / Ayytarget]]></description>
