      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵🔘WC8 / 1800 / F$M</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7PrgtyOCRbD1sOkTdoYLYYpw9t6T-02p0qcaI45S2d38prPhepIkZNT4g6q_XC6EDgwnKp0K6eNC5SZq5EEGKktOOZbbUqCLvJrPaucup7QrN9SQAT9gI076hB87Tz7xXN3r-ttLsAmo4peiZKuqEoh-ux5ogsTCc8_LzzrDavtT7pZ_b3lOhSHhSEuWyLLAaliGSQh6lr6Y_tTqoxDGHC6_S_vcV3xRlpsMVsYxXPvXS8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N18<br><br>WC8 (Wick City 8) and F$M (Fore Street Malis) are newer sets based around the Fore Street area of Upper Edmonton, within the N18 postcode. Their territory includes the Joyce Avenue and Snell's Park estates and a few other areas such as Upton Road and Raynham Avenue. The name "Wick City" comes from a fallen member known as 'Wick'.<br>They are allied with OFB and N15. They beef NPK, Edmonton/N9, Wood Green/N22, Meridian and a few other Upper Edmonton sets such as WunBlock and Zone18.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Grinz / K Wick / T Wick / YK / Scrilla]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-2386-77</styleUrl>
