Block olders and have inherited many of the original allies and old rivals of Busy Block and now beef with ELT / NOL. ELT / NOL are allied with nearby Andover, Crouch Hall Court, Wray Kray, EC1, Queens Crescent, Peckwater and Cumbo. Those gangs now beef A-Team, Essex Road, Cally Road and NRB. A-Team are allies to the OFB, Essex Road, Cally Road, Hoxton, Active Gxng, NRB, FSG and CT1 gangs.  They now beef with nearby Elthorne, New Orleans, Queens Crescent, Peckwater, Cumbo and Wood Green/N22.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Gully (NOL) / LK (NOL) / 8th Ball / Future / JR / Vipex / G.B / Ghetto / Miller Matic / Ousier Tom]]></description>
