      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Edmonton / N9 / C Block</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N9<br><br>C Block (CB) are a subset of N9 based around Charlton Road, Mottingham Road and Cuckoo Hall Lane. They are allied with 3x3/BR9, 3x3/AFG, O9B, TPL/OTP and Wood Green/22. They beef GMG/AP, OFB, NPK, N15, TPL/DC8 and Hornsey. Some members have had issues with other N9 sets.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Trillz CB]]></description>
