      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Edmonton / N9 / 3x3 / BRoad / ALG</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N9<br><br>ALG (Air Lift Gang) are a recently formed subset of N9 created by rapper E1 (3x3). They are based on the Bounces Road estate. E1 was kicked out of other 3x3 subset AFG, after a video showing him being kidnapped by N9 olders. ALG have been active in the music scene recently as E1 has also recruited youngers from other sets in Edmonton such as O9B. They are allied with 3x3/AFG, TPL/OTP and Wood Green/22. They beef GMG/AP, OFB, NPK, N15, TPL/DC8 and Hornsey. Some members have issues with fellow N9 sets O9B and 3x3/AFG. <br><br>Associated Rappers} E1 / Busy Grr / Mulli]]></description>
