      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Edmonton / N9 / 900 / 9Double0 / 41st Side</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N9<br><br>900/9Double0/41st are a subset of N9 based on the Barbot estate (a.k.a 41st Side) as well as nearby Edmonton Green, Osward Place and nearby Croyland Road. They are allied with 3x3/BR9, 09B, TPL/OTP and Wood Green/22. They beef GMG/AP, OFB, NPK, N15, TPL/DC8 and Hornsey. Some members have had issues with other N9 sets.<br><br>Associated Rappers} A1fromthe9]]></description>
