      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Edmonton / N9 / 3x3 / AFG / AfghanO</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N9<br><br>AFG (All Fuckeries Gang) also known as AfghanO (Afghan Only) is a subset of N9 based on the Beaconsfield estate (Afghan estate). They are allied with 3x3/BR9, 09B, TPL/OTP and Wood Green/22. They beef GMG/AP, OFB, NPK, N15, TPL/DC8 and Hornsey. Some members have issues with fellow N9 set ALG.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Rowdy / ZT / MSplash / Drilla / Ds / 38]]></description>
