      <Placemark>
        <name>WunBlock / Zone18 / deadmonton</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Edmonton N18<br><br>WunBlock/Zone18 are based on the Gloucester Road, Empire Parade and Weir Hall Road estates in Upper Edmonton, within the N18 postcode. The older generation from this area, from the late 2000s and early 2010s, were known as 'Edmonton Grey Gang'. The Grey Gang were also known as 'Wun-8' and GMD (Gun Man Down). They identified with dark grey colours. They were active around Fore Street, Scott House, Beck House and on the Weir Hall, Joyce Avenue and Snells Park estates. They were allied with nearby 'Red Brick' and known for a fierce rivalry with the 'Dem Africans' (DA). WunBlock/Zone18 are allied with NPK, GMG/AP, TPL/DC8 and Hornsey/V8. They beef WC8, OFB and N15 as well as historical rivals Edmonton/N9.<br><br>Associated Rappers} SP Carlito / T & S]]></description>
