      <Placemark>
        <name>🟠Broad Lane / BL / 12</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Haringey, Tottenham N15<br><br>Broad Lane (BL) are a small set who are based on the small estates around Broad Lane in Tottenham, within the N15 postcode. They are mostly of Latino/Portuguese/Angolan origin. They are just one of over a dozen smaller street gangs located in the Tottenham area that identify with their local estates and small blocks in N15 and N17. Broad Lane first emerged as an independent set during the mid 2000s after the break ups of larger alliances like the Tottenham Mandem (TMD).<br><br>Associated Rappers} ALVEZ / ACE / CDot / RL / KayLee / Pablo12K / Zill1 / Chosen / KW]]></description>
