      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵7th / LLR / Harvist7</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Islington, Holloway N7<br><br>7th, also known as LLR (LongLiveRom/RomsWorld), are a small trapping set based on some small estates in the Holloway area such as the Harvist, Lorraine and Holloway estates, within the N7 postcode. The set are allied with some nearby sets such as Andover, Elthorne, New Orleans and CHC. '7th' are known to beef some local sets such as Essex Road, Cally Road, Wood Green, Hoxton, A-Team and NRB.]]></description>
