      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫🔴Finchley / 197

https://web.archive.org/web/20120502201019/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/north-london-gangs/graveyard-fam</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Barnet, Mill Hill NW7<br><br>Finchley 197 are a small street gang who are active in the Finchley area of North London (N2/N3/N12). They are the younger generation to a gang known as 'Graveyard Family' (GYF). They are most active on the Grange and Strawberry Vale estates. Finchley began as a group of teens who had referred to themselves as K9 from 2005. They were at the time one of a growing number of newer London gangs, in outer, suburban, areas that are located in areas much less deprived than typical places associated with street gangs.<br><br>Historically Finchley have been loosely allied with OFB, NPK, Hornsey/V8 and 9th Street. They beef 3BP, Queensbury, Wood Green/N22 and TPL/OTP. The youngers are also based in Mill Hill and have issues with 9th Street and Hendon.<br><br>Associated Rappers: Jamz / YoungBoyPsycho / Devious / MD / #212 ST / #212 Nikah / K Dizzy]]></description>
