      <Placemark>
        <name>BHP / BullyHill</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Enfield, Bush Hill Park EN1<br><br>BHP (Bush Hill Park) are a small street gang who are based on the Bush Hill Park estate in Enfield, within the EN1 postcode. They also chill around Bush Hill Park station and all the way up to the A10. They are known to flag brown. They used to be cool with N9 and Wood Green back in the 2000s, and beefed AP. Currently they beef AP/Skengfield/3rdSide, EnnyTown, 3x3 (AFG x ALG), 09B, C-Block and NPK.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Kayos / KLoose / Cardz / Dimz]]></description>
