    <Folder>
      <name>East London</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Fellows Court

https://web.archive.org/web/20120103095255/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/fellows-court</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Haggerston E2<br><br>Fellows Court Gang (FCG) who are also known as the Forever Fellows Riders (FFR) are a street gang located on the Fellows Court estate in the Haggerston area of Hackney, within the E2 postcode. The current younger generation from Fellows Court are also known under the banner of "Anything For Doe" (AFD). Historically the Fellows Court estate had always been closely affiliated with nearby Hoxton Boys, with both gangs taking on the rival London Fields Boys, although both the areas fell into conflict during the early 2010s and are now fierce rivals. The younger generation tend to be allied with London Fields, EC1, Stoke Newington and A-Road. They beef Hoxton, Holly Street, Homerton, Pembury, Whiston Road and Bethnel Green.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Dubsy / Monst / Sosa / D.Crooks / Alpo / Young Dubsy]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2801-77</styleUrl>
