              </coordinates>
            </LinearRing>
          </outerBoundaryIs>
        </Polygon>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Hindle House </name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Dalston E8<br><br>The Hindle House Thugs are a small street gang based on the Hindle House estate in the Dalston area of Hackney within the E8 postcode. Hindle House are affiliated with both the A-Road and London Fields gangs. Hindle House have conflict with the Soldiers of Shakespeare and nearby Somerford Grove.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-000000-2601-77</styleUrl>
        <Polygon>
          <outerBoundaryIs>
