      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴🔵Thatched House Thugs

https://web.archive.org/web/20120311225114/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/thatched-manz</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5_Ysnuy7Lo1m3Kl1xR8HIqH5yBFL30_TIHB2NrHlZ2JkLDSokQUg6FZzUje_X0WDVhdoA7_HphqT0ajTW8xsuYVYDSEBKpjrEdmDo9hX8otodgtQPS-YkXdDodNn-KCh2QIm81-7ZLHVboJJA0HfAbxohA3iEBhisnEBjQ9scKatmTVnF21Fr3qXK-FAsb9rW20QA?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Waltham Forest, Leytonstone E15<br><br>Thatched House Thugs are a small street gang based on the Avenue Road estate located in Leytonstone on the border of Newham and Waltham Forest who identify with red and blue colours. They beef the Loyal Soldiers from Leytonstone. The area has historically been allied with the Stratford, Plaistow, Woodgrange and Chadd Green areas.]]></description>
