      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴⚫LS / Loyal Soldiers / Leytonstone</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Waltham Forest, Leytonstone E11<br><br>LS (Loyal Soldiers) are a large street gang who are based in Leytonstone on both Cathall and Sansom & Acacia estates. The gang was created through the merger of the two Local gangs "Cathall Boys" from the Cathall estate and "AC Crew" from Sansom & Acacia estate. The LS name can can stand for both 'Loyal Soldiers' and 'Leytonstone'. LS beefs Thatch House, Beaumont, Boundary, Drive & Marlowe and 7th.  The gang also come into conflict with Mali Strip.<br><br>Associated Rappers} TBoy / Y.Pulse]]></description>
