      <Placemark>
        <name>🟢Boundary </name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5eibCe5I8kBdGSEBOq7F3OxnIQuVJaX60cWbB0Atom0Mm6tNAqTK2BJIgL9rxL_GIaM6BjnYTC7fgMaP3JaecwlfutHb9zsfrN4olP1_fDz0xi6l2rXhj57_zepPpwYoKJJmH8siUfY6QjwPCUqKMIg-GvwbqlpuWWJtUyNpvRSP7n_2ZA0e8pHlq_USIqBMcc_bw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Waltham Forest, Walthamstow E17<br><br>Boundary are a small street gang based around the Boundary estate located in Walthamstow within the E17 postcode. They were affiliated with nearby Beaumont, Coppermill, and Drive & Marlowe forming a 'Green Gang' alliance. They are allied with Drive & Marlowe and Mali Strip.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Skitz / Killa]]></description>
