      <Placemark>
        <name>Selrack (ARG)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Waltham Forest, Chingford E4<br><br>Selrack, also known as ARG, are a small street gang based on Aldriche Way estate in Highams Park, within the E4 postcode. The name of 'Selrack' comes from Selwyn Avenue, a street in their territory. They beef Chinghall, 8th and Drive & Marlowe.<br><br>Associated Rappers} KT / Kash]]></description>
