      <Placemark>
        <name>🔘🔵Bethnal Green (BG / BGM)

https://web.archive.org/web/20120207023811/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/bethnal-green-massive</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Bethnal Green E2<br><br>'Bethnal Green' (BG), known as 'Bethnal Green Massive' and 'Busy Getting Money' (BGM), are a mixed Black and Bengali street gang located around the Bethnal Green area of Tower Hamlets, within the E2 postcode. The older Bengali 'Bethnal Green Massive' included the small sets, like the 'White Flatz' (WF) based on Minerva estate and the 'Turin Street Massive' (TSM) based around Turin Street. Bethnal Green gangs have been known to have an alliance with the Bengali 'Forest Gate Massive' and rivalry with gangs in the E1 postcode and parts of E2, within neighbouring Hackney, especially Fellows Court and Whiston Road.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Grindzy / Bandido / Damage / Rico2Up]]></description>
