        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Whitechapel E1<br><br>'Brick Lane Massive' (BLM), also sometimes referred to as 'Brick Lane Mafia', are a predominantly Bengali street gang based around Brick Lane in the Whitechapel area of Tower Hamlets, within the E1 postcode.]]></description>
