        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Whitechapel E1<br><br>Brady Street Massive (BSM) are a Bengali street gang who are based around Brady Street in the Whitechapel area of Tower Hamlets, within the E1 postcode. They are allied with Cleveland. They beef Cannon Street and Bethnal Green.]]></description>
