        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Whitechapel E1<br><br>Cleveland, formerly known as Cleveland State Massive, are a small Bengali street gang based around Cleveland Way in the Whitechapel area of Tower Hamlets, within the E1 postcode. They are allied with Brady. They beef Cannon Street and Bethnal Green.]]></description>
