        <name>Globe Town (GT)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Globe Town E2<br><br>'Globe Town' (GT) who are formerly known as the 'Globe Town Massive' (GTM), are a predominantly Bengali street gang who are based on the Cranbrook estate and surrounding streets in the Globe Town area of Tower Hamlets situated within the E2 postcode. They beef 'YTB' and 'AV'.]]></description>
