        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Whitechapel E1<br><br>Cannon Street Posse (CSP), also known as the Cannon Street Massive (CSM), are a large Bengali street gang based around the Cannon Street area of Whitechapel in the borough of Tower Hamlets, within the E1 postcode. They beef Cleveland, Brady and Globe.]]></description>
