        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Stepney E1<br><br>Stepney Posse (STP) are a large Bengali street gang based on the Ocean estate in the Stepney area of Tower Hamlets, within the E2 postcode. The younger generations of the old gang have used variations in their gang name, including the acronym STP which stands for the 'Stepney Tear-Up Posse', 'Stepney Thug Passion' or 'Stepney Terror Posse'. The gangs current generation are also known simply as 'Ocean'.]]></description>
