      <Placemark>
        <name>Aberfeldy Village (AV)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Poplar E14<br><br>'Aberfeldy Village' (AV), who are formerly known as 'Aberfeldy Massive', are a mixed Black and Bengali street gang based in the Aberfeldy Village area of Poplar in Tower Hamlets, within the E14 postcode. They beef 'Willcrookz', 'IOD', 'YTB', 'BG' and 'Globe Town'.]]></description>
