      <Placemark>
        <name>Stroudley Walk Boys</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Bow E3<br><br>The Stroudley Walk Boys are a Bengali street gang based around Stroudley Walk in Bow. They are also sometimes known as the Bow boys. Their main rivals are the Burdett Dangerous Thugs and there has been numerous violent exchanges between the BDT and Stroudley Walk Boys (also known as Bow Boys) who are located literally down the street from one another although divided seemingly by the line that separates E3 and E14.]]></description>
