      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵I.O.D</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X788-Xx-Q1Oa3-f7ZUlMPsGpd__RjaqIifVpfeObt4XQn3Malpftpa1VL2NkVGt0duDth2RCVKO0shqvoFNkRohup8xe2ztSSx5YArgXw9lyhVsVOCIcdK9M5BLbKIkRJj11TmMsGKyf8i8tpQk5JgMbXO8sLwKtmnjPwW0E8imbqC3uXohBsnGfKSu9RB8Rljrui0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Isle of Dogs E14<br><br>I.O.D also known as Goon Squad are a black and mixed race street gang who are based on the Isle of Dogs which is now predominantly dominated by Bengali street gangs. They are one of the only black and mixed race street gangs in Tower Hamlets Borough which is dominated by the Bengali gangs. They rep blue bandanas as historically their main rivals had been the Devons Road Bloods and the Roman Road Bloods from Bow. They now beef 'Brownfieldz', 'AV' and 'YTB'. The I.O.D gang are primarily active on the Samuda estate and in and around Glengarock Avenue and Tiller Road. In the past there have been several smaller, mostly Bengali street gangs on the island including:<br><br>Timberwharves Massive (TWM) are a Bengali gang located around the Timberhwarves estate, on the Isle of Dogs. They clash with I.O.D, a predominantly black and mixed race gang based around Glengarock Avenue and Samuda estate.<br><br>The Tiller Road Boys (TRB) are a street gang based around Tiller Road in the Millwall area on the Isle of Dogs.<br><br>Harbinger Massive (HM) are a small Bengali street gang based around Harbinger Road on the Isle of Dogs.<br><br>Cubitt Town Massive (CTM) are a Bengali gang who are based around Cubitt Town on the Isle of Dogs. They are also known as 'Town Soldiers' (TS).<br><br>Associated Rappers} TLoose (OTB) / Damage]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-3001-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X788-Xx-Q1Oa3-f7ZUlMPsGpd__RjaqIifVpfeObt4XQn3Malpftpa1VL2NkVGt0duDth2RCVKO0shqvoFNkRohup8xe2ztSSx5YArgXw9lyhVsVOCIcdK9M5BLbKIkRJj11TmMsGKyf8i8tpQk5JgMbXO8sLwKtmnjPwW0E8imbqC3uXohBsnGfKSu9RB8Rljrui0?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
