        <name>🔵Kingsmead</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4gI__9eC7N3BwDwYfLn0TTSLpbEyNqxTmuhhzJmulUxX9_eYAYQ62hW-39bek8KqbICOdOOAUexss5SfsAImXlKPT-_IGntfP_qUlzjcvCZY0butMcsrT0iWEH9cojncfwXy_wt6M_dJd8hc5aQOVPvHD6xDS8SEVceCIY1OWY3W6VsAoao7UN4dn5LxcmE4cLsKo?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hackney, Homerton E9<br><br>Kingsmead are a small street gang who are based on the Kingsmead estate in Homerton within the E9 postcode in Hackney. Kingsmead are known to identify with dark blue colours and are closely affiliated with London Fields. They beef with Homerton, Kingshold, Pembury and Holly Street<br><br>Associated Rappers} T9 / Z9]]></description>
