      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵7th / BWC

https://web.archive.org/web/20120302021539/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/e7-crips</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5ykUmbe-AlL_IISPwhrTjfGQUMVWyhXa4vBv8Pk9S1ybU-yXa_zMyxayf5XiEFxMoRd-RiXlDX7hk6m9jkuZFagTThYfc59oszZrTpv2CqW-8-tesdXURnUAZSIn8HZRK0MEoh9HU5jEO1E-7LNMiDaOVs5yv6w7KUIrX8MJv__Q1Qk2yk96NtTZvwdh8DnXtVDZQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Newham, Forest Gate E7<br><br>7th are a large street gang who are based in the Forest Gate area, within the E7 postcode.  They are also known as 'Gaza' and 'Gate'. 7th gang are mostly active on the estates around Woodgrange Road and Blackwater Close, where their gangs two sets, 'Woodgrange' and 'BWC', are located. They identify with the colour blue, and used to be known as 'E7 Crip Gang' (ECG). E7 Crips formed around 2003 and were composed of a mixture of street gang cliques such as the 'Smooth Money Makers' (SMM), 'Eastside Gorilla Click' (EGC), 'E-Block' and a younger 'Woodgrange' generation, as well as music crews in the area like the 'Kamikaze Crew' and the 'Mobb'd Out Crew'. The Crips identity and their association with the colour blue was instigated through rivalry with nearby 'Maryland Bloods' although their conflicts with nearby Maryland had only really involved certain cliques within their gang, and was not really an area wide conflict. 7th are allied with CGE, 15th, M15 and Manor Park who form 'Northside Newham' (NSN) They beef Custom House, Canning Town and Beckton from 'Southside Newham' (SSN). They also beef nearby Loyal Soldiers.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Yanko / Stickup / Broadday]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-3949AB-2801-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5ykUmbe-AlL_IISPwhrTjfGQUMVWyhXa4vBv8Pk9S1ybU-yXa_zMyxayf5XiEFxMoRd-RiXlDX7hk6m9jkuZFagTThYfc59oszZrTpv2CqW-8-tesdXURnUAZSIn8HZRK0MEoh9HU5jEO1E-7LNMiDaOVs5yv6w7KUIrX8MJv__Q1Qk2yk96NtTZvwdh8DnXtVDZQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
