      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴M15 / Maryland </name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X71Cm8R8V8QvyynCx46Xxobek6IFaZ-KetIJvdxKU8UOEjwJbYVP7yFo9ZF65W2ISYoFYjAzPvCKGCoItJGqeQWSJdyzx0Nxtruj-FnOkfcqxs5RJ7cJ35MERl0ojkWlh8YwSb6RQ9rZzsFV-h0I7ppmnHRcluxKf1X5oOyyDoyA4uQ6ZxYKw87Pbv8tv4sq8vR0_w?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Newham, Maryland E15<br><br>Maryland, also known as 'Maryland Bloods' and 'M15', are a street gang located in the Maryland area of Stratford, within the E15 postcode.  The gang formed in the early 2000s, and identified as Bloods. Maryland Bloods gang had historically come into conflict with E7 Crips, Thatched House, Stratford, Chadd Green, Custom House and Canning Town. 'Maryland' are currently allied with 7th, 15th, CGE and Manor Park who form a 'Northside Newham' (NSN). Their main rivalry is with Custom House, Canning Town and Beckton gangs who now form a 'Southside Newham' (SSN) alliance.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2701-120</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X71Cm8R8V8QvyynCx46Xxobek6IFaZ-KetIJvdxKU8UOEjwJbYVP7yFo9ZF65W2ISYoFYjAzPvCKGCoItJGqeQWSJdyzx0Nxtruj-FnOkfcqxs5RJ7cJ35MERl0ojkWlh8YwSb6RQ9rZzsFV-h0I7ppmnHRcluxKf1X5oOyyDoyA4uQ6ZxYKw87Pbv8tv4sq8vR0_w?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
