      <Placemark>
        <name>🟡Mountford</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6Si1JsFPjxSFlQuYbujYKi9-VKvMctBzMgAUzZLmV64yvLJ-mBrrAr9rIyrS_lboSUF0laSdLBrIdQWbexd9RDbzqLYWQyunYRCV36znLFkkyXZHQQSPJ5EswfwtSjDpBLDDFgWME5zd6O6ASIO3btUR2SL5V2V2-NAVPen_Y6W1nKaD6HA2THjST2xJ-mDVIj1bI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Hackney, Dalston E8<br><br>Mountford (MF) are a small street gang who are based on the Mountford estate around the once notorious 'frontline' area of Sandringham Road in the Dalston area of Hackney, within the E8 postcode.   They are allied with A-Road and London Fields. They come into conflict with Pembury, Holly Street, Kingshold, Homerton, Mothers Square and Hoxton.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FFEA00-2501-77</styleUrl>
