      <Placemark>
        <name>YTB</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Mile End E3<br><br>The 'Young Towers Boys' (YTB) are a street gang based in the Mile End area of Tower Hamlets borough based within the E3 postcode. They are mostly active around Eric Street. They are a predominantly Somali gang and they are one of the few non Bengali gangs within the Borough of Tower Hamlets, which is dominated by Bengali street gangs. They beef with CHR, I.O.D, AV. Globe, Cleveland, Willcrookz, Limehouse and E3/Roman Road ]]></description>
