      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Northwold</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Upper Clapton E5<br><br>Northwold are a small street gang based on the Northwold estate, in the Upper Clapton area of Hackney, within the E5 postcode. They beef Southwold, Springfield, Manor House, Stamford Hill, Homerton and Holly Street.]]></description>
