      <Placemark>
        <name>Stoneydown</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Waltham Forest, Walthamstow E17<br><br>Stoneydown are a small street gang who are based around Stoneydown Close in the Walthamstow area, within the E17 postcode. They are allied with BHR, Priory Court and Beaumont.]]></description>
