      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴OC</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4DrH0UJZpU2flIDjIxaPlar-0aOqXNOB40F8qfxKLNb5uTvbSgXXWrDRxY78h1Ok-h0pZLzemGtIbL8YDQXxNat4CQ5TypkpjFYKeUeCSvBYI3O3GMVoplys_jNv6tS0a_tOHNHXoQp52uJxAgQl7j1ijtfxv_dcSefzRurjPaMdvDOR9U5avDQexEQmDHdhrX53VV?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Waltham Forest, Leyton E10<br><br>OC (Oliver Close) are a street gang based on the Oliver Close estate in Leyton, within the E10 postcode. They formed in the late 1990s and from the mid 2000 into early 2010s were part of the 'Piff City' alliance with Chingford. Their group included sets such as M-Block (Marconi Road) and BDG (Blood Gang). They beef Beaumont, Boundary, Coppermill, Drive & Marlowe and Priory Court.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2601-122</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4DrH0UJZpU2flIDjIxaPlar-0aOqXNOB40F8qfxKLNb5uTvbSgXXWrDRxY78h1Ok-h0pZLzemGtIbL8YDQXxNat4CQ5TypkpjFYKeUeCSvBYI3O3GMVoplys_jNv6tS0a_tOHNHXoQp52uJxAgQl7j1ijtfxv_dcSefzRurjPaMdvDOR9U5avDQexEQmDHdhrX53VV?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
