      <Placemark>
        <name>🔘Priory Court (PCB)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4G-Ely32TsC13dqNz-6lZ-NMclL1zLmgqY0rJsYEQHrZNI-IYQvEt3Utxk1Xt9UaUAQ9wg1dnCwqp0Xgb0YAHwGjlV8acDd35hNtjIrr3AXV1LV_sBIYoXLzFPRtJSLeXkTLZgWibobWS0kr06yY6b3JVMJNwF_-tbCECQalb6LGhQWh4NEug-ttrm8WYCHBKuVrI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Waltham Forest, Walthamstow E17<br><br>The Priory Court gang are based on the Priory Court estate situated in the Higham Hill area of Walthamstow within the E17 postcode. Priory identify with the colour grey and were initially known as 'Priory Court Grey Gang'. Sets within 'Grey Gang' had included the 'Shanklin Youngers' and 'Get Money Daily' (GMD). The current generation of the gang are known as the 'Priory Court Boys' (PCB), or simply as 'Highams Hill'. Priory Court have historically been allied with Hornsey. They are allied with Stoneydown, Blackhorse, Beaumont, Boundary, Selrack and Hornsey/V8. They beef Mali Strip, Chinghall, Shrublands, Drive & Marlowe and Coppermill.<br><br>Associated Rappers} R£MINGTON / LMoney / Juice / Shakes / Tyno Got It ]]></description>
