      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Manor Park / 12th / OM</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X67ACPUg38OHINgCJ-kY1pCYZEesTlGhEQFpB8uFGxx6wnKzE4v9njIM2HSXyKAl9WZ7ccvS_3FBL87gE2LrRhZNS8wJbKhNLCChu1hBqrAM3Z6NgqR5CBdvccL7kGxLWlgX0M3qBF0mZ9VyFn-CGQCJTCwrEuf8lEEyERFxHQtoqLG-Xw9wMvJOsxfBcTYJVvL_XA?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Newham, Manor Park E12<br><br>Manor Park/12th, also known as OM which can be translated as 'Original Manor' or 'Only Manor', are a street gang who are based on the Little Ilford estate in Manor Park, within the E12 postcode. The older generation set are known as Sq (Square) which refers to Warrior Square on the Little Ilford estate. They are loosely allied with nearby 7th, 15th, CGE and M15 to form 'Northside Newham' (NSN). Their main rivals are 1st/Drillford but they also beef Beckton, Custom House and Canning Town who form 'Southside Newham' (SSN).<br><br>Associated Rappers} M12 / Farmer / Business]]></description>
