      <Placemark>
        <name>🟣🔘8th / Woodford</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Redbridge, Woodford IG8<br><br>8th are a street gang who are based on the Orchard estate (formerly known as Broadmead estate) and Glengall Road estate in the Woodford area, within the IG8 postcode. They are allied with Chinghall. They beef Selrack.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Billz / Khaos / EK]]></description>
