      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Southwold / Upper Clapton / 5th</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Upper Clapton E5<br><br>Certified Southwold Road (CSR) are a street gang who are based on the estates around Southwold Road in the upper Clapton area of Hackney, within the E5 postcode. They are now more commonly referred to as 'Upper Clapton', or 5th. They are affiliated with nearby Spring Block. They beef the gangs from Gilpin Square, Stamford Hill and Manor House.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Rimzee / Dutchavelli / Trim / Frogzy / Creepa / Frontline]]></description>
