      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫Springfield / Upper Clapton / 5th</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Upper Clapton E5<br><br>'Springfield', often known as 'Spring Block',  are a small street gang based around Springfield Road blocks on the Webb and Fawcett estates, in the Upper Clapton area of Hackney, within the E5 postcode. They are now more commonly referred to as 'Upper Clapton', or '5th'.  They are closely affiliated with nearby Southwold. They beef the gangs from Gilpin Square, Stamford Hill and Manor House.]]></description>
