      <Placemark>
        <name>Murder Mile</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Hackney, Clapton E5<br><br>The Lower Clapton Road together with Upper Clapton Road running through the Clapton area of Hackney, within the E5 postcode was given the nickname "Murder Mile" during the late 1990s and early 2000s due to the very high number of murders, and shootings, in the area. Although the area has now began to be gentrified gang members still sometimes refer to the area as "Murder Mile".]]></description>
