      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴E3 / Roman Road / OBlock</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4V41Hro-gkWRlO_GzS2W7Uo6A__kqLz6cJKcGB4u8Kz8zm6ind03oHOhJamsjjgDsR88e-C7fl5lhJ8BoWt2udSRvnPP0avhhqr_Nxtvg-PddGFHHyo805oTPEj9osGdWxiMitxcwxAfrRqvwmZPkvfQCS5vwvqxHf97Z44jo_BxBOs5g6hWdsJbC7bdHlsy8EjuQO?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Tower Hamlets, Bow E3<br><br>The "E3 Bloods" are located around the Bow area of Tower Hamlets, within the E3 postcode. The "E3 Bloods" consists of 'Devons Road Bloods' also known as DRF (Devons Road Family) located around Devons Road on the Lincoln estate and the 'Roman Road Bloods' based on the estates around Roman Road. They are also linked with smaller sets based around Grafton House and Ennerdale House located in the nearby Mile End area.  "E3 Bloods" sets are one of the only black gangs in Tower Hamlets which is now dominated by Bengali street gangs.  In the past they have been affiliated with London Fields in Hackney. They beef IOD, YTB, CHR and Bethnal Green. The younger generation from the Roman Road and Old Ford area is now dominated by a Bengali set known as OBlock.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-FF5252-2401-122</styleUrl>
