      <Placemark>
        <name>🔘Canning Town / CTB / 16th

https://web.archive.org/web/20120314010702/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/grey-town-canning-town</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X409txXHT5cnGQzBQ4Maz3MaLZtA1yNFlZqM_oLdRCCGFaA6Ey-tGSW0uLzDe68v4sE0P6C9bED1DRbi8qY1gim1BgMi8Qtj39l-nmBwWfglMeJfWOxt_Tf-Jyf6WPA1szstKlZSbD7hiwC2U2hyY4eXxi3g98vSFHlckOOvHILzBoGm3I_6MG-SqvfTiY6e2I3mFk?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Newham, Canning Town E16<br><br>Canning Town (CT) are a small street gang situated around Canning Town, within the E16 postcode. They are known as CT,  which can be translated as 'Canning Town', or as 'Crime Town' and CTB which stands for 'Canning Town Bullies' and 'Canning Town Boys'. Canning Town is often known as 'Grey Town' and the Canning Town gang were originally known as 'Grey Gang'. Canning Town and the allies Custom House are also known as 'Hood 16', or as '16th'.<br><br>Canning Town has only really since the mid 2000s come to have an identifiable gang in terms of gang definers such as gang colours and gang names, like other parts of Newham. Historically the area has been swamped with traditional old school gangsters and organised criminals. The street gang 'Canning Town Mandem' or otherwise known as 'Grey Town' followed on from the previous gang known as the 'Jeeperz', whose 'youngers' would became known by the name 'Black Rage'.  The 'Jeeperz' were a large street gang located in the western half of Newham, largely within the E16 postcode in Canning Town and parts of Plaistow in the early 2000s with membership from those two areas, as well as Stratford and Beckton. Members would later move to other cliques. Some became Beckton olders whilst others joined the music crew 'Kids in da Hood'. Some members carried on with the 'Black Rage' set, which during 2007 became known as 'Grey Town'. During 2006/2007 there was also a younger 'Canning Town' set known as GMG (Get Money Gangsters).<br><br>'Canning Town' are closely connected to the Custom House and Silvertown areas nearby, whilst their oldest generations are connected to a wider range of areas across the borough The current generation are now part of "Southside Newham" (SSN) with allies Custom House and Beckton. They beef the 7th, CGE, M15, 15th and Manor Park gangs from "Northside Newham" (NSN).<br><br>Associated Rappers} YP / Knizz / Ktall / MK]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#poly-424242-2501-77</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X409txXHT5cnGQzBQ4Maz3MaLZtA1yNFlZqM_oLdRCCGFaA6Ey-tGSW0uLzDe68v4sE0P6C9bED1DRbi8qY1gim1BgMi8Qtj39l-nmBwWfglMeJfWOxt_Tf-Jyf6WPA1szstKlZSbD7hiwC2U2hyY4eXxi3g98vSFHlckOOvHILzBoGm3I_6MG-SqvfTiY6e2I3mFk?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
