      <Placemark>
        <name>🟣🔘GGE / CH / CTB / 16th

https://web.archive.org/web/20120314010702/http://sites.google.com/site/londonstreetgangs/gang-lists/east-london-gangs/grey-town-canning-town</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Newham, Canning Town E16<br><br>GGE are a large street gang based around Custom House and Canning Town, within the E16 postcode. They formed after the break up of 16th and are primarily the older and more established members from Canning Town and Custom House. They are a part of 'Southside Newham' (SSN) with the nearby allies Beckton. They beef with 7th, CGE, M15, 15th and Manor Park in 'Northside Newham' (NSN).<br><br>Associated Rappers} Yxng Bane / K Rose / GBM / Banko / AJ / TB / Skrilla]]></description>
