      <Placemark>
        <name>🔵1st/Drillford / LOX-LEY (MOD)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Redbridge, Ilford IG1<br><br>1st/Drillford (GYD) are a street gang who are situated around the Loxford Lane and Ley Street areas of Ilford, within the IG1 postcode. The older generation are known as "LOX-LEY". The Loxford Lane faction are also known as "Money Comes Easy" (MCE) whilst their Ley Street faction are known as "Mainly on Doe" (MOD). '1st/Drillford' are affiliated with another local set of mainly Afghans referred to as "Ilford Station Afghans" (ISA) active around Ilford station and Cranbrook. The gang are also allied with Beckton, Barkingside and GBlock. Their main rivals are Manor Park, but they also beef OCM/Hainault and CBT.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Daff / Hunter / Gully / SP / S1 / Blacka / Lzino / Sho Psycho / Klumzi / Th3rty6ix / Bailiff / Giddy]]></description>
