      <Placemark>
        <name>🟠OCM / Hainault</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X66ilvdBXefgvX4Ivd14eM0obS2M-Nmpd6Y-kJsGq_zUdCYOnwCibh2itWaF_fqDh1SzFcmW0i8bHwL7gqmZBnJLwS_bMKWdY39xHr4z5DxKnbL2lik_vkcfFKaS6YQ_pCRJjfEHIN2y-iZjNSCK9OZCfufOri4PvEIeXU20ZGkoVTu605Pak5nibQyegie4CFDGF-1?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Redbridge, Hainault IG6/IG7<br><br>OCM/Hainault are based around Hainault, within their IG6/IG7 postcodes. In the past the gang from Hainault were known as 'HQ', which stands for 'Hustle Quick'/'High Quality'. They often identified with the colour of orange and were often referred to as the "Orange Gang". They are allied with Horrid Hill and beef with 1st/Drillford and Barkingside.<br><br>Associated Rappers} Aggz]]></description>
