      <Placemark>
        <name>🟤CBT / Harts Lane</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Barking & Dagenham, Barking IG11<br><br>'CBT' (Certified Barking Tappers) are a large street gang from Barking, within the IG11 and RM8 postcodes. They are based on the Harts Lane estate in Barking and Academy Way estate near the larger Becontree estate, in the Dagenham area. They also have another set who are active around the Laindon area of Basildon (Essex). They are allied with TGB. They beef with GBlock, ASB, 1st/Drillford and 109/Dagenham. The Laindon set beef 268 (Essex).<br><br>Associated Rappers} Sosa / YR / Spinna]]></description>
