      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴ASB</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5Icym-JSkkXEdynSsN72ERQvPaDOVDhCS2TQkXA3ANr4J3_PqOA9GLTjSHoLAUWXTIDS-ILLP6osP0x9HCxW2t-pKaUpdBoQARmSOXOyEYB3wk3mAs_GyNpxPIKt7bdccRrhk6guuLexuliPltaoyXvfiN1Q9p3EEYHtp8DO9nQFuDwLjrgr5YwyBlWOlIudR7F_B3WwpbSZ9YqZ88DCj4Lazkdm7qcoZgTB4YbCL36gtz?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>London Borough of Barking & Dagenham, Barking IG11<br><br>ASB, also referred to as TVE (Thamesview Estate) are a small street gang mainly situated on Thamesview estate in Barking, within the IG11 postcode. Much of their membership is drawn from nearby Newham and Dagenham.  They are a fairly newly formed set allied with GBlock, MTM and SYS. They beef with CBT, TGB, 109/Dagenham, Horrid Hill, Beckton and Custom House.<br><br>Associated Rappers} AR / Nino / NBoogie / Rackz]]></description>
