      <Placemark>
        <name>GBlock (GB)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Barking & Dagenham, Barking IG11<br><br>GBlock (GB) are a street gang based on the Gascgoine estate in Barking, within the IG11 postcode. The older generation on the estate in the late 2000s up to early 2010s were known as "Set Gang". They are allied with 1st/Drillford, SYS and ASB. They beef with CBT and 109/Dagenham. They share their estate with an Albanian gang known as the 'Hellbanianz'. The rapper "Potter Payper" is originally from the estate.<br><br>Associated Rappers} NoMercy / BlackTrap / JM / Murda / Flex]]></description>
