      <Placemark>
        <name>⚫🟢C17 / GTM</name>
        <description><![CDATA[South Ockendon, Thurrock, Essex RM15<br><br>'C17' are a street gang who are based around Grays, notably on the Seabrooke Rise estate, South Ockendon and Chafford Hundred located within Thurrock Borough in Essex within the RM15/RM16 and RM17 postcodes. Their younger generation are known as 'GTM'. 'C17' are allied with 268 (Basildon), NTG (Purfleet) and have close ties through family connection with 410 (London). They are known to beef RM/Romford (London), 109/Dagenham (London), GBlock (London) and also 12Block (Southend).<br><br>Associated Rappers} Valenti / Zedz / KP / Y.Valenti / Chukz]]></description>
