These sets are based in the northern part of Dagenham within the RM8 and RM9 postcodes.<br><br>The Dagenham Village area, within the RM10 postcode, is home to a set known as 'SYS/System' who are based around Ibscott Close. They are allied with GBlock and ASB. They beef 109/Dagenham and CBT. <br><br>Associated Rappers} Associated Rappers} Tabz / YingThat / Lil Gr]]></description>
