      <Placemark>
        <name>🔴AFG / SCD</name>
        <description><![CDATA[London Borough of Newham, East Ham E6<br><br>AFG and SCD are two sets based around the centre of the London Borough of Newham, within the E6, E7 and E13 postcodes. Their main territory is around Plashet park and Milton Avenue. 'AFG' are a mainly Afghan set, however the gang also contains some other Asian and Black members. 'SCD' have Portuguese origins with the most active members within the gang repping 'AFG' or 'MTM' in Dagenham and Chadwell Heath who they are affiliated with.<br><br>Associated Rappers} KKalas]]></description>
